description:
Experience the Pinnacle of Capability and Comfort in the 2022 GMC Sierra 1500 SLT. This exceptional full-size pickup is engineered to conquer any challenge, while delivering a refined and luxurious driving experience that will exceed your expectations.

Boasting a powerful EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine and a smooth-shifting 10-Speed Automatic transmission, the Sierra 1500 SLT delivers impressive performance and efficiency, with 14 MPG in the city and 19 MPG on the highway. But this truck is more than just raw power – it's also packed with a wealth of premium features that elevate your driving experience to new heights.

• SLT Convenience Package: Includes ventilated front seats, wireless charging, Bose premium audio, and more
• 3 Years of OnStar & Connected Services Plan: Enjoy the convenience and peace of mind of OnStar's suite of safety and security features
• Navigation System: Easily navigate to your destination with the intuitive GMC Infotainment System
• Preferred Equipment Group 4SA: Adds a wealth of premium features to enhance your driving experience

The Sierra 1500 SLT's stunning White exterior and well-appointed interior exude an air of refined sophistication, while the rugged 4WD capability ensures you can tackle any terrain with confidence. The spacious cabin offers ample room for passengers and cargo, with a wealth of thoughtful amenities to keep everyone comfortable and connected.

Experience the ultimate in truck capability and luxury with the 2022 GMC Sierra 1500 SLT. This exceptional vehicle is the perfect blend of power, technology, and refinement, making it the ultimate choice for discerning truck buyers. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why the Sierra 1500 SLT is the perfect vehicle to elevate your driving experience.

Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and practicality with this 2021 Mazda CX-5 Sport. Boasting a sleek Snowflake White Pearl Mica exterior, this all-wheel-drive crossover SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience.

• Fresh Cabin Filter
• Fresh Oil Change
• Detailed Inside and Out
• Multi Point Safety Inspection Performed by Certified Technician
• Non-Smoker
• Fresh Filters

Vehicle Detailed

With its SKYACTIV® 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine and 6-speed automatic transmission, this CX-5 delivers an impressive 24 city/30 highway MPG, making it both efficient and enjoyable to drive. The all-wheel-drive system provides confident handling in a variety of road conditions, while the four-wheel independent suspension ensures a smooth and responsive ride.

Packed with an array of advanced features, this CX-5 Sport offers the perfect balance of technology and convenience. Enjoy the convenience of keyless entry, steering wheel-mounted audio controls, and a rearview camera. Stay connected with the MAZDA CONNECT infotainment system, featuring Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration.

Safety is a top priority, with features like dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, ABS brakes, and electronic stability control to keep you and your passengers secure. The Exterior Parking Camera Rear and Auto High-beam Headlights add an extra layer of confidence and convenience.

Slip behind the wheel of this well-equipped 2021 Mazda CX-5 Sport and experience the perfect blend of style, performance, and practicality. With its impressive features and meticulous attention to detail, this crossover SUV is sure to exceed your expectations.

Our exclusive One Owner 2021 Tesla Model Y AWD Long Range is versatile and efficient in Red Multi-Coat. Motivated by Dual Electric Motors with a 75kWh battery for 384hp sent to a 1 Speed Automatic transmission for lightning-like acceleration. As youd guess, the interior also boasts an impressive array of technology, anchored by a 15-inch touchscreen supporting BluetoothÂ®, WiFi compatibility, wireless charging, and a 14-speaker audio system for immersive sound.

description: This 2021 Mazda CX-5 AWD Grand Touring has 45,642 miles, a clean CarFax history, and one previous owner. It is a well-maintained compact SUV that combines engaging driving dynamics with a premium interior and modern features. The all-wheel-drive system enhances traction and confidence in a variety of road and weather conditions, making this CX-5 suitable for daily driving as well as weekend adventures. Under the hood, this CX-5 is powered by a responsive four-cylinder engine paired with a smooth shifting automatic transmission. The powertrain offers a balanced combination of performance and efficiency, delivering confident acceleration and composed handling. Mazdas tuning emphasizes a connected driving experience, and the AWD system contributes to stability on highways and winding roads alike. Inside, the Grand Touring trim elevates the cabin with high-quality materials, comfortable seating, and thoughtful design details. The front seats are supportive for long drives, and the rear seats offer ample space for passengers. Standard features include leather upholstery, heated front seats, a power-adjustable drivers seat, dual-zone automatic climate control, and an intuitive infotainment system with a large display screen. Connectivity options such as Apple CarPlay and Android Auto help keep drivers and passengers connected on the go. Cargo space in the CX-5 is generous for its class, and the rear seats fold easily to provide additional room for gear, luggage, or other items. The overall interior layout feels spacious and functional, with storage solutions that accommodate everyday needs. Safety is a priority in the CX-5, with a suite of driver assistance technologies designed to help provide added peace of mind. Features such as blind spot monitoring, rear cross traffic alert, lane departure warning, and adaptive cruise control work together to support safer driving in a range of conditions. In summary, this 2021 Mazda CX-5 AWD Grand Touring with 45,642 miles, a clean CarFax report, and one owner offers a compelling blend of performance, comfort, and technology. It is an excellent choice for anyone seeking a reliable and stylish SUV with refined driving characteristics and modern amenities.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and performance in this exceptional 2021 Nissan Rogue SL. With its sleek black exterior and meticulously detailed interior, this SUV is sure to turn heads wherever you go.

Key features include:
• Navigation System
• Leather Upholstery
• Bluetooth Connectivity
• Backup Camera
• Safety Inspected
• Fully Detailed

This Rogue SL also boasts a host of premium amenities, such as a Chrome Rear Bumper Protector, Power Liftgate, and Black Splash Guards, elevating your driving experience to new heights.

Powered by a 2.5L I4 DOHC 16V engine and paired with a smooth-shifting CVT with Xtronic, this Rogue delivers an impressive 26 MPG in the city and 34 MPG on the highway, making it an exceptional choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin that offers the perfect balance of comfort and convenience. Sink into the plush leather-appointed seats, enjoy the warmth of the heated steering wheel, and let the Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control keep you and your passengers perfectly comfortable.

The advanced NissanConnect infotainment system, complete with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration, puts a world of connectivity and entertainment at your fingertips. Stay informed and entertained on every journey.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like Automatic Emergency Braking, Blind Spot Warning, and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert working tirelessly to help keep you and your loved ones secure.

This 2021 Nissan Rogue SL is a true gem, offering an unbeatable combination of style, technology, and performance. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by all that this exceptional SUV has to offer.

Discover exceptional value with this 2021 Volkswagen Atlas 3.6L V6 SE w/Technology — a spacious, dependable SUV available now in Columbia, SC. Powered by a smooth and capable 3.6L V6 gasoline engine with AWD, this Volkswagen Atlas combines confident performance and composed handling for family trips, daily commutes, and weekend adventures. Priced to sell, this Volkswagen Atlas offers the best price on the market for a well-equipped, one-owner SUV with a clean CARFAX history.

Versus the previous generation of Range Rover Sport, this new SUV is faster and significantly more agile, thanks to its much lighter, all-aluminum construction. With major improvements in interior packaging and design, it is a more pleasant place for passengers, providing a luxurious, refined place. Compared to other models in its class, the Range Rover Sport doesn't make as much of a sacrifice in ride quality for handling and off-road prowess, while its feature set and luxurious cabin appointments are a step above some in the same price range. Key rivals include the BMW X5, Porsche Cayenne, INFINITI QX70 and Cadillac Escalade. This well-maintained Pilot has been meticulously cared for, with a clean CARFAX history and low mileage for its age. It's the perfect blend of practicality and luxury, ready to elevate your driving experience.

Imagine the possibilities with this 2015 Honda Pilot EX-L. Imagine the adventures you'll embark on, the memories you'll create, and the convenience you'll enjoy every day. This SUV is a true gem, and it's waiting for you here at our dealership.

description:
2015 Mercedes-Benz GL 450 4MATIC Premium Package - 85,127 Miles - Original MSRP $72,180
This 2015 Mercedes-Benz GL 450 4MATIC delivers full-size luxury SUV comfort with refined power, advanced features, and timeless design. Finished in classic Iridium Silver Metallic over Black MB-Tex upholstery, it was originally configured with an MSRP of $72,180, and includes key factory options that elevate the driving experience.

Under the hood, a responsive 3.0L biturbo V6 engine pairs seamlessly with 4MATIC all-wheel drive, offering smooth acceleration and confident all-weather traction. The Premium Package (P01) adds some of the most desirable luxury enhancements, making every mile more comfortable and connected.

Factory Options & Highlights:
- Premium Package (P01) Includes Navigation, Blind Spot Assist, Keyless-GO, and more
- 19" Twin 5-Spoke Wheels Refined design meets confident stance
- Eucalyptus Wood Trim Warm, elegant cabin detail
- Iridium Silver Metallic A classic Mercedes-Benz finish
This GL 450 has had just two owners and shows a strong service history with regular maintenance performed by authorized Mercedes-Benz service centers, including recent oil changes, brake service, and a comprehensive tune-up in late 2024. A minor cosmetic incident was reported in 2017, affecting the front and right-front, but there were no structural or airbag-related issues.

With 85,127 miles, this GL is consistent with age-related use and still offers excellent long-term value especially considering a comparably equipped new GLS today would exceed $85,000.

At Mercedes-Benz of North Olmsted, we specialize in delivering a premium, streamlined buying experience for both local and out-of-state clients. Our team is highly experienced in nationwide delivery and out-of-town sales, ensuring a smooth, professional transaction wherever you are.

At Mercedes-Benz of North Olmsted, we're transforming the dealership experience. Our Worry-Free Pricing ensures a hassle-free process no pressure, no games just transparent, market-based pricing from the start, giving you complete confidence while you shop.

description: Experience luxury and power in this Beige 2015 GMC Yukon Denali 4x4 SUV. Jim Taylor Chevrolet is proud to offer this well-equipped Chevrolet, delivering the comfort, capability, and features drivers expect for everyday driving.

• White Diamond Tricoat exterior color
• Navigation System
• Magnetic Ride Control Suspension Package
• Bose Centerpoint Surround Sound 10-Speaker System
• Heated and Cooled Front Seats
• Power Folding and Adjustable Heated Outside Mirrors

This 2015 Chevrolet Suburban LTZ is a true standout in the full-size SUV segment. With its powerful 5.3L V8 engine and smooth 6-speed automatic transmission, this Suburban delivers impressive performance and efficiency, achieving up to 23 MPG on the highway. The RWD drivetrain provides confident handling and a comfortable ride, while the Magnetic Ride Control suspension package enhances the driving experience.

Inside, you'll find an abundance of premium features that elevate the Suburban's luxury and convenience. The Bose Centerpoint Surround Sound audio system provides a concert-hall listening experience, while the heated and cooled front seats ensure year-round comfort. The power-adjustable pedals, steering wheel, and driver's seat with memory settings allow you to find your perfect driving position with ease.

The Suburban's spacious interior offers seating for up to eight passengers, along with ample cargo room for all your gear. The power liftgate and hands-free access make loading and unloading a breeze. The advanced technology features, including the Chevrolet MyLink infotainment system with navigation, keep you connected and in control on the road.

Safety is also a top priority in this Suburban, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver assistance technologies. Features like Forward Collision Alert, Lane Departure Warning, and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert help you stay aware of your surroundings and react quickly to potential hazards.

Whether you're transporting your family, hauling oversized items, or embarking on an adventure, this 2015 Chevrolet Suburban LTZ is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and convenience that this exceptional SUV has to offer.

Shop with confidence at Jim Taylor Chevrolet in Rayville, Northeast Louisiana, proudly serving drivers from Monroe, Bastrop, Delhi, Winnsboro, and surrounding areas. We offer a strong selection of new Chevrolet vehicles and quality pre-owned options, along with assistance for financing, trade-ins, and test drives. Visit us in Rayville or explore our inventory online at jimtaylorchevrolet.com to find the vehicle that fits your needs.

description:
Experience the power and versatility of the 2015 Ford Expedition EL Limited. This impressive SUV boasts a commanding presence and a wealth of premium features that elevate your driving experience.

- Local Trade
- Equipment Group 301A
- GVWR: 7,720 lbs Payload Package
- Voice-Activated Navigation System w/HD Radio
- Power Moonroof
- Power Deployable Running Boards

Under the hood, the 3.5L V6 engine and 6-speed automatic transmission deliver a smooth and responsive performance, while the 4WD system ensures confident handling in all conditions. With an EPA-estimated 20 MPG on the highway, this Expedition EL provides the perfect balance of power and efficiency.

The exterior of this Expedition EL Limited showcases a sleek and sophisticated Black paint finish, complemented by the polished 20-inch aluminum wheels and chrome accents. The power-deployable running boards make it easy to access the spacious interior, which is outfitted with premium features like the voice-activated navigation system, SiriusXM satellite radio, and a premium Sony sound system.

Comfort and convenience are at the forefront, with dual-zone automatic climate control, heated and cooled front seats, and a power liftgate. The Blind Spot Information System (BLIS) and rear load-leveling suspension further enhance the driving experience, ensuring a smooth and safe journey.

The 2015 Chevrolet Tahoe 4WD 4dr LTZ is an impeccable blend of luxury and performance wrapped in a sophisticated Black exterior. With its robust 5.3L 8-cylinder engine, this vehicle ensures power and reliability in all driving conditions. Its Jet Black interior exudes elegance and comfort, making it a luxurious environment for both driver and passengers alike.Equipped with four-wheel-drive capability, the Tahoe offers exceptional off-road performance, perfectly complemented by its premium 22" wheels. Inside, the vehicle boasts a third row of seating, providing ample space for family and friends. The Sun Entertainment and Destinations Package, along with the rear-seat Blu-Ray/DVD entertainment system, ensures entertainment for all passengers during long journeys.The 2015 Chevrolet Tahoe LTZ prioritizes safety with features like blind spot monitoring, forward collision warning, and lane departure warning. Both heated and ventilated seats offer customizable comfort, while the power tilt-sliding sunroof adds a touch of openness to the cabin. The inclusion of a premium sound system enhances every drive, and the intuitive Chevrolet MyLink Radio with navigation keeps you on the right path. Further supported by parking assist, rain-sensing wipers, and a towing package, this SUV is as versatile as it is luxurious. Experience the pinnacle of luxury and capability with this exceptional 2015 Cadillac Escalade Platinum Edition. This stunning SUV boasts a commanding presence on the road, combining cutting-edge technology, unparalleled comfort, and uncompromising performance.

• Power-Retractable Assist Steps with LED Lighting
• Driver Assist Package
• Driver Awareness Package
• Platinum Package
• Preferred Equipment Group 1SD
• Theft-Deterrent Package

Beneath the sleek, silver exterior lies a powerful Vortec 6.2L V8 SIDI engine mated to an 8-speed automatic transmission, delivering exceptional power and efficiency. The 4-wheel drive system ensures confident handling in any conditions, while the Magnetic Ride Control Suspension provides a remarkably smooth and composed ride.

Climb inside and be enveloped in the luxurious cabin, featuring full semi-aniline leather Nappa seat trim, a microfiber sueded headliner, and unique exotic wood accents. The Bose Centerpoint Surround Sound System and Cadillac CUE infotainment system with embedded navigation provide an unparalleled multimedia experience, while the Reconfigurable 4-Color Head-Up Display and Rear Seat Entertainment System keep you and your passengers entertained and informed.

Safety and driver assistance features abound, including Forward Collision Alert, Automatic Emergency Braking, Lane Departure Warning, and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, ensuring peace of mind on every journey. The Adaptive Full-Speed Range Cruise Control and Automatic Safety Belt Tightening further enhance the driving experience.

This 2015 Cadillac Escalade Platinum Edition is a true masterpiece of engineering and design, blending uncompromising luxury, cutting-edge technology, and exceptional capability. Experience the pinnacle of SUV excellence – schedule a test drive today and discover the difference for yourself.

Unlock the Luxury of the 2015 Buick Enclave Premium Group

Introducing the 2015 Buick Enclave Premium Group - a premium SUV that seamlessly blends refined style, advanced technology, and exceptional performance. This stunning Enclave is the embodiment of Buick's commitment to crafting vehicles that elevate your driving experience.

Boasting an impressive array of premium features, the Enclave Premium Group is tailored to exceed your expectations. Key highlights include:

• Experience Buick Package with power moonroof, 20" wheels, and 4500 lbs. Trailering Package
• Crimson Red Tintcoat exterior with a bold, commanding presence
• Bose premium sound system for an immersive audio experience
• Heated and cooled front seats for year-round comfort
• Cutting-edge safety technologies like Forward Collision Alert and Lane Departure Warning

Beneath the Enclave's refined exterior lies a powerful 3.6L V6 engine paired with an advanced all-wheel-drive system, delivering responsive performance and confident handling. With an EPA-estimated 22 MPG highway, this SUV strikes the perfect balance between power and efficiency.

Thoughtfully designed to accommodate your active lifestyle, the Enclave Premium Group offers seating for up to seven passengers and ample cargo space. The power liftgate and rear parking sensors make loading and unloading a breeze, while the articulating headlights and trailer hitch package enhance the vehicle's versatility.

Step inside and you'll be surrounded by premium materials, including perforated leather-appointed seating and a heated steering wheel. The intuitive infotainment system, complete with navigation and Bose audio, keeps you connected and entertained on every journey.

This 2015 Buick Enclave Premium Group represents an exceptional value in the luxury SUV segment. With its impressive list of features, refined driving dynamics, and timeless style, it's a vehicle that will elevate your daily commute and weekend adventures alike.

We invite you to experience the 2015 Buick Enclave Premium Group for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this exceptional SUV should be your next automotive investment.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and performance in this stunning 2015 Ford Edge Titanium. This meticulously maintained SUV is a true standout, offering a captivating combination of sophisticated design and advanced features that will elevate your driving experience.

Boasting a sleek, eye-catching Red exterior, this Edge Titanium commands attention wherever it goes. Under the hood, the powerful EcoBoost 2.0L I4 GTDi DOHC Turbocharged VCT engine delivers an impressive 20 city/28 highway MPG, ensuring exceptional efficiency without sacrificing power.

• Local Trade
• Equipment Group 302A
• Technology Package

Indulge in the unparalleled comfort and convenience of this well-equipped Edge Titanium. Sink into the luxurious perforated leather-trimmed heated and cooled bucket seats, and enjoy the warmth of the heated steering wheel and rear seats on chilly days. The panoramic Vista Roof floods the cabin with natural light, creating an airy and inviting atmosphere.

Stay connected and entertained with the cutting-edge technology features, including the voice-activated touch-screen navigation system, Integrated SiriusXM Traffic & Travel Link, and the powerful 12-speaker Sony audio system. description:
Experience the Pinnacle of Luxury with the 2015 GMC Yukon Denali

Commanding the road with its bold presence and uncompromising capabilities, the 2015 GMC Yukon Denali is a true masterpiece of engineering and design. This exceptional full-size SUV offers a winning combination of power, sophistication, and advanced technology, making it the ultimate choice for discerning drivers who demand the best.

• Clean Carfax
• Touring Package
• 20" Chrome Wheels

Beneath the Yukon Denali's striking exterior lies a heart of pure power. The EcoTec3 6.2L V8 engine, paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission, delivers an exhilarating driving experience, effortlessly conquering any terrain with its 4-wheel drive capabilities. With an impressive fuel efficiency of 14 city/21 highway MPG, this SUV strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality.

Step inside the Yukon Denali, and you'll be enveloped in a world of unparalleled luxury and comfort. The spacious cabin is adorned with premium materials, including genuine wood accents and perforated leather-appointed seating. The driver and front passenger can enjoy the ultimate in personalized comfort with heated and ventilated front seats, while the rear passengers bask in the warmth of the heated rear seats.

The Yukon Denali's advanced technology features elevate the driving experience to new heights. The Head-Up Display projects vital information directly into your line of sight, allowing you to keep your eyes on the road. The Bose Centerpoint Surround Sound system delivers a concert-hall-quality audio experience, while the IntelliLink infotainment system seamlessly integrates your smartphone with intuitive voice controls and navigation.

Safety is paramount in the Yukon Denali, with a comprehensive suite of driver assistance technologies. The Rear Cross-Traffic Alert and Side Blind Zone Alert systems help you navigate with confidence, while the Safety Alert Seat provides tactile warnings to keep you aware of your surroundings.

Whether you're embarking on a family adventure or tackling the demands of your busy lifestyle, the 2015 GMC Yukon Denali is the ultimate companion. Experience the pinnacle of luxury, performance, and technology in this exceptional SUV. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why the Yukon Denali is the perfect choice for you.

description:
Elevate Your Driving Experience with the 2015 GMC Yukon XL Denali

Discover the perfect blend of power, luxury, and versatility in the 2015 GMC Yukon XL Denali. This exceptional SUV is ready to take your driving experience to new heights, offering a commanding presence on the road and a wealth of premium features that will leave you captivated.

• Bose Centerpoint Surround Sound 10 Speaker System
• Hands Free Power Liftgate
• Head-Up Display
• Power-Adjustable Pedals
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Heated Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel
• Passive Entry System
• Power Tilt-Sliding Sunroof
• Rear Seat Blu-Ray/DVD Entertainment System
• Wireless Charging

Boasting an EcoTec3 6.2L V8 engine and 8-speed automatic transmission, the Yukon XL Denali delivers a thrilling and efficient driving experience. With its impressive 4-wheel drive capability, this SUV is ready to tackle any terrain with confidence, while the Magnetic Ride Control Suspension Package ensures a smooth and responsive ride.

Step inside the Yukon XL Denali and be enveloped in luxurious comfort. The premium leather-appointed seating, heated and ventilated front seats, and heated rear seats provide exceptional comfort, while the Bose audio system and dual-zone climate control ensure a personalized driving environment. The power-adjustable pedals and memory settings allow you to tailor the interior to your preferences for a truly customized experience.

Convenience and connectivity are at your fingertips with features like the Head-Up Display, wireless charging, and the intuitive IntelliLink infotainment system with built-in navigation. The Rear Cross-Traffic Alert and Blind Spot Monitoring systems heighten your awareness on the road, while the Hands Free Power Liftgate and Remote Start make loading and unloading a breeze.

Whether you're embarking on a family adventure, towing a trailer, or simply enjoying the daily commute, the 2015 GMC Yukon XL Denali is the perfect companion. Elevate your driving experience and discover the exceptional capabilities of this premium SUV. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and experience the Yukon XL Denali for yourself.

The **2015 Chevrolet Suburban LT** is an excellent pick for buyers who need a **true full-size SUV** that combines **spacious seating, robust towing capability, and a well-appointed interior**. Powered by a **355-hp 5.3 L V8** and backed by a truck-based frame, it offers **strong performance and a towing capacity of up to around 8,000–8,300 lbs** — ideal for hauling trailers, boats, or campers with confidence. The LT trim adds thoughtful features like **forward-collision alert, lane-departure warning, Chevrolet MyLink infotainment, Bose premium audio, power-adjustable seats, and available luxury upgrades**, giving you comfort and convenience for long family trips or daily driving. With room for up to eight passengers and **impressive cargo space behind the third row**, it stands out as a **versatile and capable SUV** for large families, adventurers, or anyone needing serious hauling and seating capacity without moving up to a luxury price bracket

Convenience
  • Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. It's stop/go feature automatically brings the vehicle to a stop if traffic stops and resumes distance pacing cruise when traffic starts to move again. Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, your ultimate co-pilot.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Head-up display - Keep your head up! You don't have to take your eyes off of the road to get information from your dashboard anymore. With head-up display, important driving information - like speed and RPM's - displays on your windshield in your line of sight. Because when you're driving, the most important information lies on the road ahead. Keep your eyes on the road with head-up display.
Technology and Telematics

Unlock the thrill of off-road adventure with this exceptional 2015 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sahara. Boasting a bold red exterior and a powerful 3.6L V6 engine, this Wrangler is ready to conquer any terrain you encounter. With its impressive 4WD capabilities and a host of premium features, this Wrangler is the ultimate companion for your outdoor excursions.

Elevate your driving experience with the following impressive features:

• GPS Navigation
• Connectivity Group
• Dual Top Group
• Quick Order Package 24G
• Sunrider Soft Top
• 40GB Hard Drive with 28GB Available
• 8-Speaker Alpine Audio System with All-Weather Subwoofer

Indulge in the convenience of remote start, heated front seats, and an auto-dimming rearview mirror, ensuring your comfort and control on every journey. The Uconnect 430N infotainment system with a 6.5-inch touchscreen display keeps you connected and entertained, while the premium black sunrider soft top provides the ultimate open-air experience.

This Wrangler Unlimited Sahara is more than just a capable off-road vehicle, it's a true expression of your adventurous spirit. Imagine traversing rugged terrain, tackling challenging obstacles, and exploring the great outdoors, all while enjoying the refined comfort and advanced technology this Jeep has to offer.

With its heavy-duty suspension, traction control, and 4-wheel disc brakes, this Wrangler Unlimited Sahara is built to handle whatever the road (or trail) throws your way. The integrated roll-over protection and dual front impact airbags ensure your safety, while the power windows, remote keyless entry, and steering wheel-mounted audio controls add to the overall convenience.

Step into the driver's seat of this exceptional 2015 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sahara and unlock a world of off-road excitement. Experience the thrill of the open road and the freedom to explore, all while surrounded by the premium features and capabilities that make this Wrangler a true standout in its class.

Don't miss your chance to make this Wrangler Unlimited Sahara your own. Schedule a test drive today and discover the ultimate in off-road adventure and on-road comfort.

description:
Welcome to Dean Carter Chevrolet! We're out to change the way you feel about the car buying experience, and proud to offer our local communities in Monroe County the very best in quality, price, selection, and service. Take this 2015 Toyota RAV4 Limited for example.... Offered in RED exterior with interior, it's certain to make a great addition to your family or business! Be sure to take note of all this vehicle has to offer: One Owner! Important/Valuable Packages & Equipment Wheel Locks ($65 value)
    Display Audio w/Navigation, Entune and JBL ($785 value)
    • Includes 6.1 In. touch-screen w/integrated backup camera display, AM/FM CD player w/MP3/WMA playback capability, 11 JBL GreenEdge speakers in seven locations including subwoofer and amplifier, SiriusXM satellite radio (includes 3-month trial subscription to XM Select Package), HD Radio w/iTunes Tagging, Entune (Includes Bing and Pandora, real-time info, including traffic, weather, fuel prices, sports and stocks), auxiliary audio jack, USB port w/iPod connectivity and control, vehicle information, hands-free phone capability, phone book access, advanced voice recognition, text-to-speech w/programmed and customizable text responses, and music streaming via Bluetooth wireless technology.
    Comfort
    • Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions - That's hot. Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions provide more targeted warmth so you can get comfortable quicker in cold weather. If you have lower body pain, you might also be soothed by the heat while you drive. No matter the weather, find comfort in heated driver and front passenger seat cushions.
    Convenience
    • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
    • Power open and close liftgate - On-demand access. When your arms are full of cargo, the last thing you want to do is set it all down just to open the liftgate, then pick it all back up to load it in. By remotely opening and closing, power liftgate lets you skip straight to the loading. It also eliminates the awkward stretch to reach up for the liftgate to close it. Load and go with power open and close liftgate.
    Safety and Security
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Selective Internet access - a more focused delivery. Selective internet access allows you to tailor the features for your feed, such as sports scores, local news, or current weather. When it comes to getting what you want, selective internet access is a net gain.
    • Voice activated integrated navigation system - A to B made easy! Whether it's an errand or a road trip, the voice activated integrated navigation system will guide you to your destination. No more bulky, impossible-to-fold maps, and no more stopping to ask for directions. Just tell it where you want to go, and the voice activated integrated navigation system shows you the right way.
    Other Notable Features/Options To verify availability of this vehicle please contact our client care team at 570-992-0200 or stop by see us at 1476 Route 209 Brodheadsville PA 18322. Let us show you why Dean Carter Chevrolet is the dealership you can trust...now and in the future.

Introducing the 2014 Nissan Xterra S - a rugged and capable SUV that's ready to take on any adventure. With its powerful 4.0L V6 engine, 4-wheel drive, and impressive off-road capabilities, this Xterra is the perfect companion for your outdoor pursuits.

* 4X4

Boasting a spacious and versatile interior, the Xterra S offers ample room for passengers and cargo alike. The split-folding rear seat and available roof rack provide the flexibility to accommodate all your gear, whether it's hiking equipment, camping supplies, or sports equipment. And with features like the Bluetooth® Hands-Free Phone System, SiriusXM Satellite Radio, and steering wheel-mounted audio controls, you can stay connected and entertained on the go.

Under the hood, the Xterra's 4.0L V6 engine delivers a robust 261 horsepower and 281 lb-ft of torque, providing the power you need to conquer any terrain. Paired with a smooth-shifting 5-speed automatic transmission, this SUV offers a confident and responsive driving experience, both on and off the road.

Safety is also a top priority, with the Xterra S boasting a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features. From the anti-lock brakes and electronic stability control to the dual front and side impact airbags, you can rest assured that you and your passengers are well-protected.

Whether you're tackling the daily commute or embarking on an outdoor adventure, the 2014 Nissan Xterra S is the perfect companion. With its rugged good looks, impressive capabilities, and well-appointed interior, this SUV is sure to turn heads and make a lasting impression.

We invite you to come and experience the Xterra S for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover the true meaning of versatility and capability in an SUV. We're confident that once you get behind the wheel, you'll be ready to take on the world.

The 2015 Mercedes-Benz GLA 250 offers pros like sporty handling , a powerful turbocharged engine , stylish design, good fuel economy for its class, and available luxury features (navigation, panoramic roof, 4MATIC AWD). It's praised for its agility, sedan-like driving dynamics, and useful tech, but potential buyers should be aware of potential reliability concerns and higher maintenance costs compared to non-luxury brands, plus some interior space limitations. Pros: Performance: 2.0L turbo engine (208 hp/258 lb-ft torque) offers quick acceleration (0-60 mph in 6.9s) and fun driving dynamics, especially in Sport mode. Handling: Agile, hatchback-like feel with direct steering and good body control, great for city driving. Fuel Economy: Class-leading for AWD models (around 27 MPG combined). Style & Design: Sleek, aerodynamic, and aggressive styling distinguishes it from boxier SUVs. Features: Available with desirable tech like navigation, backup camera, premium audio, and a panoramic moonroof (often in packages). All-Wheel Drive (4MATIC): Effective and quick-reacting, providing stability in various conditions. Practicality: A useful power liftgate and adaptable rear seats (60/40 split) add versatility. Overall Appeal: The GLA 250 is great for buyers prioritizing style, brand prestige, and engaging driving dynamics in a compact luxury package, but it demands a willingness to accept potentially higher ownership costs and practical compromises. This Mercedes-Benz GLA-Class GLA 250 defines excellence in an SUV. It has the convenience of limitless boundaries paired with city sophistication. This AWD-equipped vehicle handles well in any weather condition or terrain. You'll benefit from superb handling, improved steering and excellent acceleration. Low, low mileage coupled with an exacting maintenance program make this vehicle a rare find. More information about the 2015 Mercedes-Benz GLA-Class: Mercedes-Benz enters the increasingly crowded luxury compact crossover segment with the GLA-Class. Its sedan underpinnings and small stature make it a nimble performer, with favorable comparison against completion from BMW and Audi. The high-performance GLA45 AMG takes things to a different level, however, and nothing from any manufacturer can rival it. Interesting features of this model are superb power in AMG guise, available technology and safety features, athletic handling, and Overall execution feels upscale and exclusive Accident or damage reported to Carfax

description:
Welcome to a different way to buy a car
Enough is enough. The games, the gimmicks. The endless surprises. We put an end to all of it. At Drivher Motors, we do more so you can do less. We are the anti-dealership. We think the car buying process has become ridiculous. And the client is the one who suffers. If you are looking for the lowest price car, we probably are not what you are looking for. We will never have the lowest price cars - our viewpoint is the lowest price cars tend to be the most expensive in the long-run. We create value. We aren't a car flipper or reseller - we are a value-add retailer. We do the research. We do the verifications. We have the car repaired and serviced. All so you don't have to. If that sounds good to you, you are going to love working with us for your next vehicle purchase.
- Clean Carfax/Clean title
- Warranty:
- 6 month/6k mile warranty on all vehicles
- 12 month/12k mile warranty on all repairs we had completed
- Complete satisfaction delight guarantee
- Independently inspected
- Work we had completed to get it ‘Drivher 30k road-ready‘ completed - we address preventative maintenance for the next 30k miles.
- ...more details coming soon.
- Also available:
- - Integrated wireless Apple Carplay/Android Auto
- Remote Start
- Pedal Commander/Pedal Kill Switch as theft deterrent
- OTT Tune
- Overlanding (off roading) parts and accessories
- Extended warranty available
Certification Results:
- PASSED - Vehicle History
- PASSED - Road Test
- PASSED - Engine + Transmission
- PASSED - Powertrain (4x4)
- PASSED - Suspension
- PASSED - Tires + Brakes
- PASSED - Interior Features + Functions
- PASSED - Body
- PASSED - Odors (none)
All of our vehicles are certified preowned. Why do we say come see us last...? We only carry the cleanest, gently used and well maintained cars. The first thing we do with all cars is have them inspected by an independent 5 star mechanic. If there is anything that is not as it should be, we have it fixed before the car is ever available for purchase. How confident are we in our cars? We encourage you to go see the other cars you are considering first and save us for last. You'll definitely see the difference in the cars and feel the difference in the customer experience.

This Chevrolet Tahoe gives you everything you need an automobile to be. Indulge yourself with one of the most highly crafted, most luxurious automobiles available today. Handle any terrain with ease thanks to this grippy 4WD. Whether you're on a slick pavement or exploring the back country, you'll be able to do it with confidence. Added comfort with contemporary style is the leather interior to heighten the quality and craftsmanship for the Chevrolet Tahoe LTZ. Performance, ease of use and efficiency are just a few reasons you'll love the navigation system that comes with this car. This vehicle comes with an extra bonus: past service records are included. The interior of this Chevrolet Tahoe LTZ has been through meticulous inspection and could almost pass for a brand new vehicle. Fast and exciting, this Chevrolet Tahoe LTZ is a true testament to the pursuit of automotive distinction by Chevrolet. Once you're behind the wheel of this incredible machine, you will not think twice about purchasing this vehicle. This Chevrolet Tahoe LTZ comes standard with features that are essential in the 21st Century. However, Chevrolet decided to take it one step further and add a handful of quintessential options that will undoubtedly add to this vehicle's quality and value. This Chevrolet is equipped with some of the most amazing wheels the market has to offer! Once you take this Chevrolet Tahoe LTZ for a test drive, you'll immediately realize how much of an added bonus this vehicle's upgraded wheels will provide. More information about the 2015 Chevrolet Tahoe: The Suburban and Tahoe are by far the best-selling models in their class, and they're tough rivals for the Ford Expedition, Toyota Sequoia and Nissan Armada, among just a few others. These two Chevy models are closely related in most ways--although there's a key difference: The Suburban is 14 inches longer in wheelbase and 20 inches longer overall than the Tahoe, and that results in a significantly larger third-row seat than in the Tahoe--as well as easier access to it, and more cargo space. Compared to rival models, the Chevy Tahoe and Suburban still stand out for their good ride quality and efficient engines, and they handle surprisingly well considering their size and mass. They're also very rugged and versatile, and can be outfitted for off-road toughness, tow ability, and interior luxury as needed. Chevrolet claims that the Suburban will be the most fuel-efficient model in the full-size SUV class, thanks to its standout combination of fuel-saving technologies like direct injection and active fuel management (cylinder deactivation). Although the profile of the Suburban and Tahoe haven't changed all that much, Chevy has managed to make significant improvements to aerodynamics. Yet chiseled sheetmetal and big, flamboyant wheels (up to 22 inches) help maintain a powerful look. Interesting features of this model are towing ability, Much-improved interior, relatively fuel-efficient engines, comfortable, refined ride, seating space, and versatility and toughness

description: The 2015 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sahara is a four-door variant of the iconic off-roader, balancing rugged capability with enhanced interior comfort and utility. Performance and Mechanical Engine: 3.6L Pentastar V6 delivering 285 horsepower and 260 lb-ft of torque. Transmission: Choice of a 6-speed manual or a 5-speed automatic transmission. Drivetrain: Standard part-time Command-Trac 4WD system with a manual hi-lo transfer case. Capability: Includes heavy-duty suspension with gas shocks and Dana solid axles. Fuel Economy: Approximately 16 city / 20–21 highway MPG. Interior and Technology Seating: Accommodates five passengers with cloth or available leather-trimmed heated front seats. Entertainment: Standard 8-speaker audio system (upgradable to a 9-speaker Alpine system with an all-weather subwoofer) and Uconnect system with voice command. Comfort: Features a leather-wrapped steering wheel, power windows, and locks, along with an auto-dimming rearview mirror. Cargo Space: Offers 31.5 cubic feet behind the rear seats, expanding to 70.6 cubic feet with seats folded. Exterior and Safety Design: Signature 18-inch Sparkle Silver wheels, body-colored fender flares, and tubular side steps. Open-Air Freedom: Fully removable top (hard or soft) and doors, with a fold-down windshield. Safety Features: Equipped with 4-wheel ABS, Electronic Stability Control, Traction Control, and Hill Start Assist. Utility: Standard fog lights, underbody skid plates, and a towing capacity of up to 3,500 lbs

Discover the perfect blend of off-road capability and modern convenience in this 2015 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sport. With its striking orange exterior and well-equipped interior, this Wrangler is ready to take you on unforgettable adventures while providing the comfort and technology you desire.

• Remote Keyless Entry
• Sirius XM Ready
• Bluetooth
• Cruise Control
• Connectivity Group
• Black 3-Piece Hard Top

This Wrangler comes equipped with a powerful 3.6L V6 engine mated to a 5-speed automatic transmission, delivering the perfect balance of performance and efficiency. Enjoy the freedom of 4-wheel drive as you conquer any terrain, whether you're tackling challenging off-road trails or navigating the city streets.

The interior of this Wrangler Unlimited Sport is designed with your comfort in mind. Slip into the cloth bucket seats and take advantage of features like the leather-wrapped steering wheel, chrome/leather-wrapped shift knob, and the Uconnect voice command system with Bluetooth connectivity. Stay connected on the go with the remote USB port and SIRIUS satellite radio.

For added convenience, this Wrangler is equipped with power windows, power locks, and a security alarm. The deep-tint sunscreen windows and auto-dimming mirror with reading lamp provide a touch of refinement, while the tire pressure monitoring display and vehicle information center keep you informed and in control.

Rugged and versatile, the 2015 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sport is the perfect companion for your adventurous lifestyle. With its impressive off-road capabilities and well-appointed interior, this Wrangler is ready to take you to new heights of exploration and excitement. Experience the freedom and capability that only a Jeep can provide. Visit our showroom today to take this remarkable Wrangler for a test drive and discover the thrill of owning this iconic SUV.

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2015 Cadillac Escalade ESV Platinum Edition. Boasting a sleek White exterior and a powerful Vortec 6.2L V8 SIDI engine, this full-size luxury SUV is the epitome of refined power and sophistication.

Highlighted features include:
• Power-retractable running boards with LED lighting
• 22-inch chrome 6-spoke wheels
• Driver Assist, Driver Awareness, and Platinum packages
• Reconfigurable 4-color head-up display
• Cooled center console with covered storage
• Rear-seat entertainment system with dual screens
• Adaptive full-speed range cruise control
• Automatic front and rear braking
• Lane departure warning and lane change alert

Indulge in the unparalleled comfort and convenience of the Escalade ESV Platinum. Sink into the premium Nappa leather-trimmed seats, which are both heated and ventilated for year-round comfort. The power-retractable running boards and hands-free power liftgate make entry and loading effortless.

Elevate your driving experience with the Cadillac CUE infotainment system, featuring a large 8-inch touchscreen display, navigation, and a premium Bose surround sound system. Stay connected and entertained on the go with seamless integration of your smartphone and wireless charging capabilities.

Safety is paramount in the Escalade ESV Platinum, with features like forward collision alert, lane departure warning, and a 360-degree camera system to provide you with added peace of mind. The Magnetic Ride Control suspension and 4-wheel disc brakes with ABS deliver a smooth, responsive, and confident driving experience.

This 2015 Cadillac Escalade ESV Platinum Edition is a true testament to the brand's commitment to luxury, performance, and innovation. Experience the difference for yourself – schedule a test drive today and discover the ultimate in full-size SUV refinement.

description: Our 2015 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sport 4x4 shown in a Black paint scheme, is ready to handle everything thrown its way. Powered by a 3.6 Liter V6 that produces 285hp and almost as much torque while combined with the rock-solid Dana axles managed by a 5 Speed Automatic transmission. This Four Wheel Drive will allow you to maintain civility or let you carve your path where ever you see fit while offering near 21mpg. With city streets and freeways providing an increasingly unfriendly atmosphere to standard, car-based suspensions, large tires and real ground clearance are increasingly handy for the committed urbanite. Take a look at one of the most widely recognized terrain busting, four-door vehicles in the world. This Jeep looks sharp with 17 inch alloy Fuel rims, aftermarket leveling kit with Fox shocks, aftermarket LED headlights, aftermarket hood and aftermarket side steps!Stepping in or out of most potholes does nothing more than spill your drink. This Jeep is loaded. It has full power accessories, great air conditioning, steering wheel audio controls, cruise control, and a stereo with audio auxiliary input. If you get the urge to take an open-air cruise, just remove the top, put on some shades, crank up the amazing sound system, and hit the road! A secure safety cage surrounds you, plenty of airbags protect you, 4-wheel ABS, traction control and stability control help you along the way. Our Wrangler Unlimited Sport offers all of the legendary rock-climbing ability of America's favorite off-roader, with a dose of comfort to go along for the ride! Print this page and call us Now...We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership!

With exceptional power, towing and handling, this SUV can handle anything thrown at it. Put performance, safety, beauty, sophistication and all the right amenities into a car, and here it is! Now you can own luxury without the luxury price tag! At home in the country and in the city, this 2015 4WD Cadillac Escalade Luxury has been wonderfully refined to handle any occasion. Smooth steering, superior acceleration and a supple ride are just a few of its qualities. With less than 89,844mi on this Cadillac Escalade, you'll appreciate the practically showroom newness of this vehicle. More information about the 2015 Cadillac Escalade: The Escalade is a luxury-vehicle icon--both as one of the most luxurious and noteworthy American luxury vehicles and as a capable truck beneath it all. Cadillac says that the Escalade's EPA highway rating of 21 mpg is 17 percent higher than that of the previous model, and significantly better than that of either the Mercedes-Benz GL550 or Lexus LX 570. Yet the Escalade can reach 60 mph in less than six seconds--shockingly quick for a vehicle of its size and weight. The Escalade's trailer-towing rating of up to 8,300 pounds (or 8,100 pounds for the ESV) is better than that of the Land Rover Range Rover or either of those other models. Separately, the new front-seat airbag is unlike anything else in this class, potentially providing an added assurance in some types of accidents, while all the active-safety features might help keep you from ever getting in one. This model sets itself apart with smooth, quiet ride yet responsive handling, Stylish, iconic look and bold profile, advanced safety technology throughout, warm, inviting cabin trims, and strong V8 truck performance This vehicle includes a Money-Back Guarantee* and has passed our precise inspection process. Meticulously maintained and backed by a comprehensive vehicle history report, this 2015 Mercedes-Benz GLK 350 represents an exceptional value in the pre-owned luxury SUV market. With its blend of style, performance, and advanced safety features, it's the perfect choice for discerning drivers seeking a truly exceptional driving experience.

We invite you to experience the exceptional quality and craftsmanship of this 2015 Mercedes-Benz GLK 350 for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover the unparalleled joy of Mercedes-Benz ownership.

description: Experience luxury and capability with this Black 2015 Cadillac Escalade ESV Premium. Powered by a robust EcoTec3 6.2L V8 engine paired with an 8-speed shiftable automatic transmission and RWD, this SUV delivers both performance and comfort. Enjoy superior convenience with a power-operated rear liftgate, remote engine start, and proximity entry system. The spacious interior features premium leather upholstery, heated and cooled front seats, a heated steering wheel, and power-adjustable pedals. Stay connected and entertained with the Cadillac CUE infotainment system on an 8-inch touchscreen, navigation, Bluetooth, Bose premium audio, rear Blu-Ray/DVD entertainment, and hotspot Wi-Fi. Advanced safety includes surround view camera, front automatic emergency braking, lane keeping assist, blind spot monitoring, and rear cross traffic alert. Adaptive cruise control, magnetic ride control suspension, and rear air suspension ensure a smooth ride. This Escalade also offers a power moonroof, third-row seating, separate rear audio, and rear seat entertainment-perfect for families or road trips. Meticulously maintained, this Escalade is ready for its next adventure.

Elevate your driving experience with this 2015 Cadillac SRX Luxury Collection, now available in Santa Maria, CA. This refined luxury crossover pairs a powerful 3.6L V6 engine with an AWD drivetrain for confident handling and smooth performance in varied road conditions. Well-equipped for comfort and convenience, the Cadillac SRX Luxury Collection features Automatic Climate Control, premium BOSE stereo sound, and Hands-Free Bluetooth for seamless connectivity on every journey. Safety and confidence come standard: the vehicle includes Cross-Traffic Alert to assist during parking and reversing, plus a CARFAX Clean Report confirming a well-documented history. The interior blends high-quality materials with thoughtful design, delivering supportive seating and a quiet cabin ideal for commuting or long drives. Practical cargo space and flexible seating make this Cadillac SRX versatile for family duties or weekend adventures. This Cadillac SRX is competitively priced — offering the best value in the Santa Maria area for a Luxury Collection with these features and AWD capability. Whether you prioritize performance, comfort, or safety, this 2015 Cadillac SRX meets demanding expectations while maintaining a strong ownership record. Schedule a test drive in Santa Maria, CA to experience this luxury crossover firsthand and secure an exceptional price on a meticulously maintained vehicle. Financing options available, contact us for details and to arrange a viewing.

Equipment
Engulf yourself with the crystal clear sound of a BOSE sound system in this Cadillac SRX. The state of the art park assist system will guide you easily into any spot. The installed navigation system will keep you on the right path. See what's behind you with the back up camera on it. This Cadillac SRX has a clean CARFAX vehicle history report. It is pure luxury with a heated steering wheel. Heated seats for those cold winter days are included in it. The leather seats in this unit are a must for buyers looking for comfort, durability, and style. This 2015 Cadillac SRX offers Automatic Climate Control for personalized comfort. This model's Cross-Traffic Alert: Safeguarding you from unexpected traffic when reversing. Never get into a cold vehicle again with the remote start feature on it. The vehicle features a hands-free Bluetooth phone system. Maintaining a stable interior temperature in it is easy with the climate control system.

  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
  • Mechanical
Exterior and Appearance
  • First-row sunroof - Let more of the outside in. Now you can be in the sun or gaze at the stars from the comfort of your seat, and have a more open cabin during your drive. Your first-row sunroof is a breath of fresh air.
  • First-row power express open/close sunroof - Let more of the outside in. Now you can be in the sun or gaze at the stars from the comfort of your seat, and have a more open cabin during your drive. With one touch of a button, The first-row power express open/close sunroof is a breath of fresh air.
Powertrain and Mechanical
  • Variable valve timing - Change your output. There are a lot of variables in your drive, so why should your engine always operate the same? With variable valve timing, the engine is efficient at both low and high RPM's, so you get better fuel efficiency, cleaner emissions and improved performance. Variable valve timing provides a better drive, every time.
  • Inline-4 engines produce adequate horsepower while typically offering better fuel efficiency and more economical maintenance than larger engines.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.

AutoNation Subaru Roseville is honored to present a wonderful example of pure vehicle design... this 2015 Chevrolet Tahoe LT only has 132,679mi on it and could potentially be the vehicle of your dreams! This Chevrolet includes: ENGINE, 5.3L ECOTEC3 V8 WITH ACTIVE FUEL MANAGEMENT, DIRECT INJECTION AND VARIABLE VALVE TIMING Flex Fuel Capability 8 Cylinder Engine *Note - For third party subscriptions or services, please contact the dealer for more information.* The Chevrolet Tahoe LT offers a fair amount of utility thanks to its advanced features and unique styling. It's also quite sporty, and injects an ample amount of handling chutzpah into the ridin'-high body of a family-friendly SUV. With amenities and luxuries befitting a modern day king, this splendorous coach reigns supreme. At home in the country and in the city, this 2015 4WD Chevrolet Tahoe LT has been wonderfully refined to handle any occasion. Smooth steering, superior acceleration and a supple ride are just a few of its qualities. More information about the 2015 Chevrolet Tahoe: The Suburban and Tahoe are by far the best-selling models in their class, and they're tough rivals for the Ford Expedition, Toyota Sequoia and Nissan Armada, among just a few others. These two Chevy models are closely related in most ways--although there's a key difference: The Suburban is 14 inches longer in wheelbase and 20 inches longer overall than the Tahoe, and that results in a significantly larger third-row seat than in the Tahoe--as well as easier access to it, and more cargo space. Compared to rival models, the Chevy Tahoe and Suburban still stand out for their good ride quality and efficient engines, and they handle surprisingly well considering their size and mass. They're also very rugged and versatile, and can be outfitted for off-road toughness, tow ability, and interior luxury as needed. Chevrolet claims that the Suburban will be the most fuel-efficient model in the full-size SUV class, thanks to its standout combination of fuel-saving technologies like direct injection and active fuel management (cylinder deactivation). Although the profile of the Suburban and Tahoe haven't changed all that much, Chevy has managed to make significant improvements to aerodynamics. Yet chiseled sheetmetal and big, flamboyant wheels (up to 22 inches) help maintain a powerful look. Strengths of this model include towing ability, Much-improved interior, relatively fuel-efficient engines, comfortable, refined ride, seating space, and versatility and toughness

Immerse yourself in the rich, 14-speaker BOSE Surround Sound System, stay connected with the Porsche Communication Management system, and enjoy the comfort of heated front and rear seats. The power liftgate and 14-way adaptive sport seats with memory function add convenience and personalization to your daily drives.

Beyond the impressive list of features, the Cayenne Turbo's performance is truly unmatched. The 4.8L V8 DI Twin Turbocharged engine, paired with an 8-speed Automatic Tiptronic transmission, delivers exhilarating acceleration and a thrilling driving dynamic. With its all-wheel-drive system, you'll conquer any road with confidence, whether navigating winding mountain passes or traversing inclement weather.

Boasting a CARFAX Certified history with no accidents, this Cayenne Turbo is a testament to Porsche's commitment to quality and reliability. Meticulously maintained and serviced, this vehicle is ready to provide you with years of exceptional performance and enjoyment.

description: Explore this striking 2014 Toyota RAV4 Limited, a versatile SUV that combines reliability with premium features. With only 99,139 miles on the odometer, this used vehicle boasts a sophisticated Brown Sugar Metallic exterior that turns heads, complemented by a sleek black interior designed for comfort and durability. Powered by a 2.5-liter four-cylinder engine producing 176 horsepower and 172 lb-ft of torque, it delivers a smooth ride with impressive fuel efficiency—22 mpg city and 29 mpg highway—making it an ideal choice for both daily commutes and weekend adventures. The 6-speed automatic transmission, combined with all-wheel drive, ensures confident handling across various terrains. This RAV4 is loaded with modern amenities, including a backup camera, Bluetooth connectivity, fog lights, heated seats, keyless entry, memory seats, navigation system, push-start button, satellite radio readiness, and a sunroof/moonroof, providing a luxurious driving experience. Designed for safety and security, this 2014 Toyota RAV4 Limited offers essential features to protect you and your passengers. It includes driver-side knee airbags and four-wheel anti-lock braking system (ABS) to enhance stability and control. The vehicle also features anti-lockout power door locks and auto-locking mechanisms, ensuring convenience and security at all times. These safety features work together to provide peace of mind whether you're navigating city streets or highways, making this SUV a dependable choice for families and commuters alike. 2014 Toyota RAV4 Safety and Security Features This model is equipped with knee airbags for the driver, offering additional protection in the event of a collision. The four-wheel anti-lock braking system (ABS) enhances braking performance and stability, especially in emergency situations. Power door locks include anti-lockout functionality, preventing you from getting locked out of your vehicle, while auto-locking features activate automatically to secure the doors once driving begins. Together, these safety and security measures underscore Toyota's commitment to driver and passenger safety. 2014 Toyota RAV4 Entertainment and Technology Features Stay connected and entertained on every journey with the advanced technology suite of this RAV4 Limited. It features a navigation system with real-time traffic data, helping you reach your destination efficiently. The touch-screen display, measuring 6.1 inches, provides easy access to HD radio, voice-operated controls, and various multimedia options. The sound system includes six speakers, delivering crisp audio, while auxiliary inputs such as USB and iPod/iPhone compatibility allow seamless device integration. Whether streaming music or navigating unfamiliar routes, this SUV offers modern technology at your fingertips. 2014 Toyota RAV4 Performance Features This RAV4 is equipped with on-demand all-wheel drive, providing enhanced traction and stability in diverse driving conditions. The system automatically engages all four wheels when additional grip is needed, making it suitable for both urban environments and light off-road excursions. The naturally aspirated 2.5-liter engine ensures a balanced blend of power and efficiency, while the smooth 6-speed automatic transmission delivers effortless shifting. Overall, the performance features of this vehicle emphasize versatility and confidence behind the wheel.

This 2014 Acura MDX 3.5L Technology Package SH-AWD is a remarkable SUV that combines sophisticated style, impressive performance, and a wealth of premium features to elevate your driving experience. With its sleek gray exterior and well-appointed interior, this MDX is sure to turn heads wherever you go.

Under the hood, the 3.5L V6 SOHC i-VTEC 24V engine delivers a potent 290 horsepower, mated to a smooth-shifting 6-speed automatic transmission and Acuras renowned Super Handling All-Wheel Drive (SH-AWD) system. This powertrain provides exceptional acceleration and confident handling, while also achieving an impressive 18 MPG in the city and 27 MPG on the highway.

The Technology Package elevates this MDX to new heights, offering a wealth of advanced technologies and premium amenities. Enjoy the clarity and immersive sound of the Acura/ELS Studio Premium Audio System, navigate with the integrated GPS Navigation System, and stay connected with the intuitive infotainment controls. The dual-zone automatic climate control, heated front seats, and power moonroof further enhance your comfort and convenience.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like Adaptive Suspension, Electronic Stability Control, and a comprehensive suite of airbags to provide you and your passengers with peace of mind. The Rear-View Camera and Parking Sensors make maneuvering in tight spaces a breeze.

This 2014 Acura MDX 3.5L Technology Package SH-AWD is a true testament to Acuras commitment to craftsmanship and innovation. With its exceptional performance, premium features, and timeless design, its the perfect SUV to elevate your driving experience. We invite you to visit our showroom and experience this remarkable vehicle for yourself. Let us demonstrate how this MDX can exceed your expectations and become the perfect addition to your lifestyle.

description:
Introducing the **2014 Honda CR-V LX**, a versatile and dependable SUV that excels in comfort, safety, and efficiency. This model is powered by a robust **2.4L I-4 DOHC engine**, delivering an impressive **185HP** while paired with a smooth **5-speed automatic transmission**. Perfect for family outings or weekend adventures, the CR-V LX is designed to cater to all your driving needs.

Safety is paramount in the Honda CR-V LX. With its **Rear Camera**, you can easily navigate tight spaces while ensuring you avoid obstacles that may otherwise go unnoticed. This feature acts as an extra set of eyes, enhancing your visibility when reversing. Additionally, the **Brake Assist** system is crucial for emergency situations, providing immediate stopping power by detecting panic braking and applying full force to help prevent potential accidents.

Long road trips are made more enjoyable with the **Cruise Control with Steering Wheel Mounted Controls**. This feature allows you to set a desired speed and maintain it without constant accelerator pressure, reducing driver fatigue and improving fuel efficiency. The inclusion of **Variable Valve Timing** ensures that the engine operates efficiently across different RPMs, resulting in better fuel economy and cleaner emissions.

In terms of connectivity and entertainment, the CR-V LX does not disappoint. The **Wireless Audio Streaming** feature allows you to enjoy your favorite playlists or podcasts directly from your mobile device without the hassle of cords. Furthermore, **Wireless Connectivity** facilitates hands-free calling, keeping you connected while you focus on the road ahead.

Security is also a top consideration with the **Ignition Immobilizer**, a passive system that prevents unauthorized access by ensuring only the correct key can start the vehicle. This feature provides peace of mind, knowing your vehicle is secure. The **External Memory Control** feature enhances your in-car experience, allowing easy access to your digital media from various sources.

In summary, the **2014 Honda CR-V LX** stands out as an efficient and practical SUV that combines advanced technology, safety features, and reliability. Whether you find yourself navigating busy city streets or embarking on a weekend getaway, the CR-V LX is equipped to handle your diverse needs with style and confidence. If youre seeking a dependable SUV that offers modern features and practicality, the Honda CR-V LX is an excellent choice worth considering.

Our Accident Free 2014 Jeep Wrangler Sahara 4X4 is bold and adventurous in a Black Clear Coat finish. Powered by a 3.6 Liter V6 that produces 285hp combined with Dana axles and a 5 Speed Automatic transmission that allows you to carve your path wherever you see fit. description: Step into adventure with the 2014 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon 4x4, a legendary icon in off-road capability and rugged style. With a mileage of 116,636 miles, this robust warrior is ready to conquer new terrains and create unforgettable memories. Its striking white exterior is not just a statement of elegance but a canvas of possibilities, seamlessly blending into any backdrop, whether it's the urban jungle or the heart of the wilderness. Inside, you are greeted by the luxurious comfort of tan leather seats, providing a plush sanctuary amidst the rugged outdoors. This interior is not just about comfort, it’s about durability and style, ensuring that every journey is embarked upon in utmost luxury. The spacious cabin of the Unlimited Rubicon is designed to accommodate your adventurous spirit and your crew, offering ample room for passengers and gear alike. Under the hood, the heart of this beast is a powerful 3.6L V6 engine, delivering an impressive 285 horsepower and 260 lb-ft of torque. This engine is engineered to provide you with the perfect balance of power and efficiency, making every drive an exhilarating experience. Paired with a smooth 5-speed automatic transmission, the Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon offers seamless shifts and effortless control, whether you're cruising down the highway or tackling rocky trails. What sets this Jeep apart is its legendary off-road prowess. The Rubicon is equipped with Jeep’s renowned 4x4 system, ensuring that no path is too daunting. Whether you're navigating snowy roads, muddy paths, or rocky inclines, this vehicle is designed to handle it all with confidence and ease. The Rubicon's robust suspension and high ground clearance make it a formidable force in any environment, allowing you to explore without limits. This particular model comes with manufacturer options and packages that enhance its already impressive capabilities, making it a true standout in the Jeep family. Its accolades speak volumes, having earned the prestigious Kelley Blue Book's Best Resale Value: Mid-Size SUV/Crossover award. This recognition not only highlights its exceptional durability and desirability but also reassures you of its value retention, making it a smart investment for the future. Imagine yourself at the helm of this 2014 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon 4x4, with the wind in your hair and the horizon as your destination. The thrill of adventure is just a turn of the key away. This vehicle isn’t just a mode of transportation, it’s a lifestyle choice, a declaration of freedom and exploration. Whether you’re an avid off-roader or someone who simply appreciates the versatility and reliability of a Jeep, the Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon is designed to meet and exceed your expectations. It’s not just about where you’re going, it’s about how you get there. And with this Jeep, every journey is bound to be extraordinary. Don't miss the opportunity to own this remarkable vehicle. The 2014 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon 4x4 is more than just a car, it’s your ticket to adventure. Embrace the freedom of the open road and the thrill of the unknown. Your next adventure awaits—are you ready to take the wheel?

description:
Discover the ultimate off-road companion in this exceptional 2014 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Altitude. With its rugged 4x4 capabilities, striking blue exterior, and an impressive array of premium features, this Wrangler is ready to elevate your adventures to new heights.

Boasting a remarkable list of upgrades, this Wrangler Unlimited Altitude stands out from the crowd. Key highlights include:

• Backup Camera
• Sirius XM Radio
• Bluetooth
• Cruise Control
• Four-Wheel Drive
• Tow Package
• Heated Leather Seats
• USB/AUX Input
• GPS Navigation
• Body Color 3-Piece Hard Top
• Rear Window Defroster
• Tire Pressure Monitoring Display
• Leather Steering Wheel with Black Stitch

The Wrangler Unlimited Altitude's powerful 3.6L V6 engine, paired with a smooth-shifting 5-speed automatic transmission, delivers an exhilarating driving experience both on and off the beaten path. With 16 city/20 highway MPG, this Jeep offers a compelling balance of capability and efficiency.

Elevate your adventures with the Dual Top Group, which allows you to seamlessly transition between the premium black hardtop and the classic Sunrider soft top, giving you the ultimate open-air freedom. The Quick Order Package 24L Altitude further enhances the Wrangler's style and functionality, featuring a host of premium touches like the Glossy Black Jeep Badge, Altitude Hood Decal, and Black High Gloss Exterior Mirror Caps.

Inside, the Wrangler Unlimited Altitude pampers you with a wealth of comfort and convenience features. The Uconnect 430N infotainment system with GPS navigation, SiriusXM Travel Link, and a 40GB hard drive keeps you connected and entertained on the go. Heated leather seats and a leather-wrapped steering wheel with black stitching add an extra touch of refinement.

With its uncompromising off-road prowess, striking good looks, and an impressive list of premium features, this 2014 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Altitude is the ultimate adventure-ready SUV. Experience the thrill of open-air freedom and conquer any terrain with confidence. Schedule a test drive today and discover the unparalleled capability and versatility of this exceptional Wrangler.

Vehicle Details
2014 Toyota 4Runner SR5 4WD V6 – Albuquerque's best-priced adventure-ready SUV. Rugged reliability meets everyday comfort in this iconic mid-size 4x4, equipped with a stout 4.0L V6 gasoline engine and proven Toyota durability. Whether you're commuting around Albuquerque or heading into the high desert, this Toyota 4Runner delivers confident traction and capable off-road performance. Well-equipped with modern conveniences, this SR5 includes a Back-Up Camera for safer reversing and parking, plus Hands-Free Bluetooth for seamless phone calls and audio streaming on the go. Spacious seating and versatile cargo space make it ideal for family trips, outdoor gear, or weekend projects. Solid build quality and a reputation for longevity mean this Toyota 4Runner remains a smart value for years to come. This vehicle stands out as the best-priced option in Albuquerque, NM — offering exceptional utility, dependability, and resale value at a competitive price. Clean interior, dependable V6 power, and 4WD capability make it a top pick for drivers who want an SUV that's ready for both city streets and rugged trails. Don't miss your chance to own a 2014 Toyota 4Runner SR5 with sought-after features like Back-Up Camera and Hands-Free Bluetooth, perfectly situated in Albuquerque, NM, and priced to move fast. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and experience why this Toyota 4Runner is the smart buy for adventure-minded drivers.

Equipment
See what's behind you with the back up camera on this Toyota 4Runner. Bluetooth technology is built into this Toyota 4Runner, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. This mid-size suv is painted with a sleek and sophisticated black color. The Toyota 4Runner has four wheel drive capabilities. Set the temperature exactly where you are most comfortable in the vehicle. The fan speed and temperature will automatically adjust to maintain your preferred zone climate. This unit has a V6, 4.0L high output engine. The Electronic Stability Control will keep you on your intended path. Help alleviate lower back pain with the driver seat lumbar support in the vehicle. Easily set your speed in this 2014 Toyota 4Runner with a state of the art cruise control system. Increase or decrease velocity with the touch of a button. The fog lights cut through the weather so you can see what's ahead.
