This 2014 Toyota 4Runner Limited is a remarkable SUV that combines exceptional off-road capability with premium features and uncompromising comfort. With its powerful 4.0L V6 engine, 4-wheel drive, and impressive fuel efficiency, this 4Runner is ready to tackle any adventure while keeping you and your passengers safe and comfortable.

- Navigation System
- 15 Speakers
- JBL Premium Audio System
- Power Moonroof
- Heated and Ventilated Front Seats
- Leather Seat Trim
- Power Adjustable Seats
- Garage Door Opener
- Rear-View Camera
- Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed interior that exudes quality and attention to detail. The leather-trimmed seats provide exceptional comfort and support, while the power-adjustable driver's seat and memory function allow you to find your perfect driving position. The premium JBL audio system and Entune infotainment system keep you connected and entertained on the road.

Beyond the impressive list of features, this 4Runner also boasts exceptional off-road capabilities. The 4-wheel drive system, combined with the sturdy body-on-frame construction, allows you to conquer the toughest terrain with confidence. Whether you're exploring the great outdoors or navigating the city streets, this 4Runner is up for the challenge.

With its sleek silver exterior and bold presence, this 2014 Toyota 4Runner Limited is a true head-turner. The 20-inch alloy wheels and roof rails add to the vehicle's rugged yet refined appearance, making it a standout in any setting.

Backed by Toyota's renowned reputation for reliability and durability, this 4Runner is an investment that will serve you well for years to come. With its impressive features, off-road prowess, and timeless style, this SUV is the perfect companion for your next adventure.

We invite you to experience the exceptional capabilities and premium features of this 2014 Toyota 4Runner Limited. Visit our showroom today and let our knowledgeable team guide you through all the details. We're confident you'll be impressed by this remarkable SUV and its ability to elevate your driving experience.

Lexus of Tampa Bay is honored to present a wonderful example of pure vehicle design... this 2014 Lexus RX 350 only has 97,238mi on it and could potentially be the vehicle of your dreams! The Lexus RX 350 is the benchmark all other SUVs strive to meet. With exceptional power, towing and handling, this SUV can handle anything thrown at it. Excellence, luxury and stature are just a few of the pillars this car is built upon. This Lexus RX 350 features AWD. That means power and control delivered to all four wheels for maximum grip and improved handling. This 2014 Lexus RX 350 has such low mileage it has been parked more than driven. With all records included, drive away confidently knowing the complete history of this Lexus RX 350 . More information about the 2014 Lexus RX 350: The Lexus RX is categorized as a mid-sized luxury SUV, and it still carries enough amenities and horsepower to lead the segment a full 14 years after its 1998 introduction. The RX 450h features a hybrid drivetrain that can run on batteries alone for short distances to save fuel, which equates to 28 mpg city and 32 mpg highway. The RX 350 does all right on its own, achieving 18 mpg city and 25 mpg highway. With this mid-cycle refresh, Lexus has done more than enough to keep its popular SUV more than relevant in the luxury sport utility conversation. Interesting features of this model are plenty of room for people and cargo, Smooth ride, and Lexus-worthy quiet cabin

Indulge in the thrill of off-road adventures, knowing your Wrangler Sahara 4xe is built to tackle the most challenging landscapes.

Certified by our trusted experts, this 2023 Jeep Wrangler Sahara 4xe is a true testament to Jeep's commitment to quality and innovation. With a 12-month/12,000-mile warranty, you can drive with the assurance that your investment is protected.

Discover the unparalleled capabilities of the 2023 Jeep Wrangler Sahara 4xe. Discover the exceptional 2023 Buick Envision Preferred, a versatile and sophisticated SUV that seamlessly blends style, performance, and advanced technology. With its sleek Ebony Twilight Metallic exterior and Black interior, this Envision Preferred exudes a refined and modern aesthetic that is sure to turn heads.

Boasting a robust 2.0L Turbocharged engine paired with a 9-Speed Automatic transmission and all-wheel drive, this Envision Preferred delivers a dynamic driving experience with an impressive 22 city and 29 highway MPG. Elevate your commute or weekend adventures with features like:

• Ebony Twilight Metallic Exterior
• Black Interior
• Preferred Equipment Group 1SC
• 7-Speaker Audio System with Amplifier
• Buick Infotainment System with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto
• Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
• Power Driver's Seat
• Heated Steering Wheel

With its powerful 295hp electric motor and 339ft. lbs. of torque, you'll experience a smooth and exhilarating ride every time you get behind the wheel.

But the ID.4 Pro isn't just about power, it's also about efficiency. With its 1-Speed Direct-Drive Automatic transmission, you'll never have to worry about shifting gears and can focus on enjoying the journey. And with zero emissions, you'll be doing your part to help the environment while still enjoying a dynamic driving experience.

The 2023 Volkswagen ID.4 Pro is not just a car, it's a statement. A statement of your commitment to a greener future and your desire for a thrilling driving experience. Don't wait, be one of the first to own the 2023 ID.4 Pro and be a part of the electric revolution. Visit your nearest Volkswagen dealership today and experience the future of driving.

Experience the epitome of modern SUV design with the 2023 Mazda CX-5 2.5 S Carbon Edition. This stunning vehicle combines exceptional performance, unparalleled comfort, and cutting-edge technology, making it the perfect companion for your adventures.

Boasting a suite of premium features, the CX-5 2.5 S Carbon Edition sets itself apart from the competition. Key highlights include:

• Clean Carfax One Owner
• Roof Rack Side Rails
• Black Lug Nuts & Black Wheel Locks
• First Aid Kit
• Rear Window Defroster
• Power Moonroof
• Apple CarPlay and Android Auto
• Heated Front Bucket Seats

Powered by the renowned SKYACTIV® 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine, this all-wheel-drive SUV delivers an exhilarating driving experience. With an impressive fuel efficiency of 24 mpg in the city and 30 mpg on the highway, the CX-5 2.5 S Carbon Edition offers the perfect balance of power and economy.

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed interior, featuring premium leather seating, a 10-speaker audio system, and a host of advanced technologies. The intuitive Multifunction Commander Control and 8-inch infotainment display keep you connected and in control, while the power driver's seat and dual-zone automatic climate control ensure your comfort.

Safety is a top priority in the CX-5 2.5 S Carbon Edition, with features like ABS brakes, dual front impact airbags, and an emergency communication system to give you peace of mind on the road. The Rear Parking Camera and Rain-Sensing Wipers further enhance your driving experience, making every journey a seamless and confident one.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2023 Mazda CX-5 2.5 S Carbon Edition. This exceptional SUV combines stunning design, impressive performance, and an array of premium features to deliver a truly remarkable driving experience. Visit our showroom today to test drive this exceptional vehicle and discover why it's the perfect choice for your next adventure.

As a Toyota Gold Certified vehicle, it includes outstanding warranty protection and long-term peace of mind.With all-wheel drive, this Corolla Cross is ready for changing road conditions while still delivering a smooth, comfortable ride for daily commuting. Inside, you'll find a clean, modern cabin with supportive cloth seating, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and smart storage throughout. Technology is simple and intuitive with Bluetooth connectivity, smart device integration, WiFi hotspot capability, and steering wheel audio controls.Toyota Safety Sense features like adaptive cruise control, lane keeping assist, blind spot monitoring, cross-traffic alert, front collision mitigation, and a backup camera help keep you protected on every drive. Practical, efficient, and easy to live with, this Corolla Cross LE is a great fit for drivers who want SUV flexibility without sacrificing efficiency or reliability.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with the 2023 GMC Terrain AT4. This exceptional SUV combines rugged capability, cutting-edge technology, and refined style to deliver a truly remarkable driving experience.

Highlighted features include:
• SUNROOF, SKYSCAPE POWER WITH POWER SUNSCREEN
• TECH PACKAGE (HD Surround Vision, Head-Up Display, Front and Rear Park Assist)
• TERRAIN PRO SAFETY PLUS (Adaptive Cruise Control, Safety Alert Seat, Rear Park Assist)
• SIDE BLIND ZONE AND REAR CROSS TRAFFIC (Lane Change Alert with Side Blind Zone Alert, Rear Cross Traffic Alert)
• Wireless Apple CarPlay/Wireless Android Auto
• Perforated Leather-Appointed Seat Trim with AT4 Logo
• Heated Steering Wheel
• 17" Gloss Black Aluminum Wheels

The Terrain AT4 is powered by a 1.5L DOHC engine paired with a 9-speed automatic transmission and all-wheel drive, delivering an impressive 24 city/28 highway MPG. This dynamic powertrain provides the perfect balance of power and efficiency, ensuring a thrilling yet fuel-efficient driving experience.

Step inside and you'll be surrounded by a wealth of premium features designed to elevate your daily commute. The Skyscape power sunroof with power sunscreen floods the cabin with natural light, while the Tech Package's HD Surround Vision and Head-Up Display keep you connected and aware of your surroundings. The Terrain Pro Safety Plus suite includes Adaptive Cruise Control, Safety Alert Seat, and Rear Park Assist for added peace of mind.

Comfort and convenience are paramount, with heated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and an 8-way power driver's seat with power lumbar support. The perforated leather-appointed seating with the AT4 logo adds a touch of refined style, while the wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration keep you seamlessly connected.

Whether you're tackling the daily grind or embarking on a weekend adventure, the 2023 GMC Terrain AT4 is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect blend of capability, technology, and refinement. Visit our showroom today to take this exceptional SUV for a test drive and discover the difference for yourself.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2023 Nissan Rogue SV, a versatile and well-equipped crossover SUV that's ready to elevate your driving experience. With its sleek styling, advanced technology, and impressive performance, this Rogue is poised to exceed your expectations.

Highlighted features include:

• New Tires
• Heated Seats
• Local Trade
• SV PREMIUM B PACKAGE
• Panoramic Moonroof
• Power Liftgate
• Heated Leather Wrapped Steering Wheel
• Leatherette Door Trim Inserts w/Stitch
• Rear Door Sunshades
• Rear Personal Lights
• Heated Driver & Front Passenger Seats

Powered by a 1.5L I3 Turbocharged engine, this Rogue delivers an exhilarating 201 horsepower, paired with a smooth and efficient CVT with Xtronic transmission and all-wheel drive. Enjoy impressive fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 28 MPG in the city and 35 MPG on the highway.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin, featuring dual-zone automatic climate control, a power driver's seat, and a premium Bose audio system. The SV Premium B Package adds even more luxury, including a panoramic moonroof, a power liftgate, and a heated leather-wrapped steering wheel.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like automatic emergency braking, blind-spot monitoring, and rear parking sensors to give you peace of mind on the road. The Rogue's advanced driver-assistance technologies, including ProPILOT Assist, help make every journey more confident and convenient.

Whether you're embarking on a family road trip or navigating the daily commute, the 2023 Nissan Rogue SV is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect balance of style, technology, and capability – visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this Rogue is the ideal choice for your next vehicle.

description:
Discover the perfect balance of style, capability, and technology in the 2023 Chevrolet Blazer LT. This exceptional SUV is a true standout, blending sophisticated design with advanced features that elevate your driving experience to new heights.

Boasting a striking exterior in a sleek White color, the Blazer LT commands attention wherever it goes. Under the hood, the powerful 2.0L Turbocharged engine, paired with a 9-Speed Automatic transmission and Intelligent All-Wheel Drive, delivers an exhilarating and efficient performance, with an impressive 22 city/27 highway MPG.

This well-equipped Blazer is packed with a host of desirable features, including:

• Collision Warning System
• Adaptive Cruise Control
• Heated Seats
• Apple CarPlay and Android Auto
• 4x4/4 Wheel Drive/AWD
• Convenience Package
• Driver Confidence Package
• Floor Liner Package (LPO)
• Midnight/Sport Edition
• Preferred Equipment Group 2LT

Standout highlights include the Universal Home Remote, Enhanced Automatic Emergency Braking, Wireless Charging, and the striking 18" High Gloss Black Painted Aluminum wheels. The Blazer LT also boasts a wealth of advanced safety technologies, such as Lane Change Alert with Side Blind Zone Alert, Rear Cross Traffic Alert, and Rear Park Assist, ensuring you and your loved ones can travel with confidence.

Step inside the Blazer LT and experience the premium Chevrolet Infotainment 3 Plus system, complete with SiriusXM 360L, seamlessly integrating your digital world. The spacious cabin, with its comfortable and supportive seating, offers ample room for passengers and cargo alike, making it the perfect companion for your adventures.

Whether you're navigating the daily commute or embarking on a weekend getaway, the 2023 Chevrolet Blazer LT is the perfect blend of style, capability, and technology. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this exceptional SUV.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2023 Nissan Rogue SL, a versatile and well-equipped crossover that's ready to elevate your driving experience. With its striking gray exterior, this Rogue SL boasts a powerful 1.5L turbocharged engine, paired with an efficient CVT transmission and all-wheel drive, delivering a thrilling yet fuel-efficient performance.

Indulge in the premium features that set this Rogue SL apart:

• Floor Mats w/2-Piece Cargo Area Protector
• Illuminated Kick Plates
• Black Splash Guards (Set of 4)
• Chrome Rear Bumper Protector

Beyond the impressive exterior, the Rogue SL's interior is designed with your comfort and convenience in mind. Enjoy the convenience of a power liftgate, the luxury of a power moonroof, and the added security of rear parking sensors. Stay connected with the advanced NissanConnect infotainment system, featuring seamless integration with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto.

Safety is paramount in the Rogue SL, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including emergency communication system, automatic high-beam headlights, and a rear-view camera with rear parking sensors. You can drive with confidence, knowing that your safety is a top priority.

The Rogue SL's impressive fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 28 city/34 highway MPG, means you can enjoy the open road without constantly worrying about refueling. Whether you're commuting, running errands, or embarking on a weekend getaway, the Rogue SL's versatility and efficiency will make every journey a pleasure.

Discover the perfect balance of style, performance, and practicality in the 2023 Nissan Rogue SL. Experience the joy of ownership and schedule a test drive today. We're confident that this exceptional crossover will exceed your expectations and become the perfect companion for your adventures.

description:
Experience the exceptional 2023 Volkswagen Taos 1.5T SE, a compact SUV that seamlessly blends style, performance, and advanced technology. This meticulously maintained vehicle, with just 32,376 miles, is a true standout in its class, ready to elevate your driving experience.

• McGrath Certified - 12mo/12k Mile
• Panoramic Sunroof Package
• Black Wheel Package
• Auto-Dimming Rearview Mirror
• Carpeted Mojomats
• Chrome Bumperdillo Protection Plate
• First Aid Kit
• Radio: MIB3 Composition Media AM/FM/HD
• Power Driver Seat
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls
• CloudTex & Cloth Seating Surfaces

Powered by a robust 1.5L turbocharged engine paired with a smooth-shifting 7-speed DSG automatic transmission, the Taos delivers an exceptional blend of power and efficiency, with an impressive 25 city/32 highway MPG rating. The available all-wheel-drive system ensures confident handling in all weather conditions, making this Taos a versatile companion for any adventure.

Step inside and be captivated by the Taos's spacious and well-appointed cabin. The panoramic sunroof floods the interior with natural light, creating an airy and inviting atmosphere. Heated front seats and a heated steering wheel provide comfort on chilly days, while the intuitive infotainment system with smartphone integration keeps you connected and entertained.

Safety is a top priority in the Taos, with a suite of advanced driver-assist technologies, including an Active Blind Spot Monitor and Rear View Camera, ensuring you and your loved ones can travel with confidence.

Whether you're commuting, embarking on a road trip, or navigating the urban jungle, the 2023 Volkswagen Taos 1.5T SE is the perfect companion. Its exceptional versatility, cutting-edge features, and impressive performance make it a standout choice in the compact SUV segment.

Experience the difference for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover why the Taos should be your next vehicle.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of power, style, and versatility with the 2023 Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited. This exceptional SUV is a true testament to Jeep's commitment to engineering excellence and customer satisfaction.

Boasting a striking Velvet Red Pearlcoat exterior, the Grand Cherokee Limited commands attention wherever it goes. Equipped with a robust 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine and 8-Speed Automatic 4WD transmission, this SUV delivers impressive performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 19 city/26 highway MPG.

Key features of this Grand Cherokee Limited include:

• Navigation System
• Quick Order Package 22E
• 6 Speakers
• Active Noise Control System
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM with 360L
• Air Conditioning with Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
• Power Driver's Seat with Memory Function
• Heated Front and Rear Seats
• Power Liftgate
• ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera
• Auto High-Beam Headlights
• Heated Steering Wheel

Step inside the Grand Cherokee Limited and experience the epitome of comfort and convenience. The Capri Leatherette-trimmed interior, paired with a heated steering wheel and heated front and rear seats, ensures a luxurious driving experience no matter the weather. The Uconnect 5 Nav system with a 10.1-inch display provides seamless connectivity and navigation, keeping you connected and on track.

Versatility is at the heart of the Grand Cherokee Limited. With its spacious and configurable interior, you can easily accommodate your passengers and cargo with ease. The split-folding rear seats and power liftgate make loading and unloading a breeze, while the 4-wheel independent suspension and traction control systems provide a smooth and confident ride, even in challenging conditions.

Discover the perfect balance of power, style, and technology with the 2023 Jeep Grand Cherokee Limited. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive at our dealership today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this exceptional SUV and its ability to elevate your driving experience.

This 2023 Ford Edge SEL offers a perfect blend of modern style, everyday versatility, and confident performance. Powered by a responsive EcoBoost 2.0L I-4 engine matched to an 8-speed automatic transmission and standard all-wheel drive, it delivers smooth acceleration and composed handling for city cruising, highway trips, and all-season driving. The Edge's sleek SUV profile, striking alloy wheels, and thoughtful exterior design cues make a bold statement while still being practical for daily use.

Step inside and experience comfort and convenience that elevate every drive. The spacious cabin is appointed with leather-trimmed seating, supportive front seats with available heating, and intuitive tech features like Apple CarPlay, Bluetooth connectivity, and a backup camera for seamless smartphone integration and safer maneuvering. A host of driver-assist and safety features -- including Blind Spot monitoring, lane departure warning, and rear cross traffic alert -- help you stay connected and confident on the road.

This Edge also earns the peace of mind advantage of Ford Gold Certified status, meaning it's passed a comprehensive inspection and comes with enhanced coverage for added security. The certification includes benefits such as a 172-point inspection, extended limited warranty coverage, roadside assistance, and more, giving you confidence beyond the initial purchase. Whether you're commuting, running errands, or heading out for adventure, this certified SUV is engineered to offer performance, comfort, and long-term value.

description:
Discover the perfect balance of style, capability, and technology in the 2023 Chevrolet Blazer LT. This exceptional SUV is a true standout, offering a captivating blend of modern design, advanced features, and exceptional performance.

Equipped with a powerful 2.0L Turbocharged engine and AWD, the Blazer LT delivers an exhilarating driving experience with impressive fuel efficiency. Key features include:

• Collision Warning System
• Blind-Spot Monitors
• Lane Keeping Assist
• Keyless Access with Push Button Start
• Apple CarPlay and Android Auto
• Driver Confidence Package
• Preferred Equipment Group 2LT

The Blazer LT's sleek and sophisticated exterior is complemented by a well-appointed interior, featuring premium cloth seating, dual-zone climate control, and a state-of-the-art Chevrolet Infotainment 3 Plus system. With its impressive technology, safety, and convenience features, this SUV is the perfect blend of style and substance.

Boasting a low-mileage, one-owner history and a clean CarFax report, this Blazer LT is a true gem. Meticulously maintained and in exceptional condition, it's ready to provide you with years of reliable and enjoyable driving.

At our dealership, we pride ourselves on offering a hassle-free and transparent buying experience. Our knowledgeable team is committed to helping you find the perfect vehicle to meet your needs and exceed your expectations.

We invite you to experience the 2023 Chevrolet Blazer LT for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover the perfect balance of performance, technology, and style that this exceptional SUV has to offer.

Quick Order Package 22E
    Comfort
    • Ventilated front seats -That's cool. Ventilated front seats provides targeted cool air so you and your passenger can get comfortable quicker in hot weather. Getting comfortable is no sweat when you have ventilated front seats.
    Convenience
    • Smart device and keyfob engine start control - Phone ahead. Remotely start your vehicle's engine from the key fob or your smart device, ensuring your ride is ready to go when you get in. Now you can stay comfortable inside while your vehicle gets comfortable outside, ,thanks to Smart device and Keyfob engine start control.
    • Power open and close liftgate - On-demand access. When your arms are full of cargo, the last thing you want to do is set it all down just to open the liftgate, then pick it all back up to load it in. By remotely opening and closing, power liftgate lets you skip straight to the loading. It also eliminates the awkward stretch to reach up for the liftgate to close it. Load and go with power open and close liftgate.
    Safety and Security
    • Blind spot warning - Protect your blind side. You checked the mirror, looked over your shoulder and still nearly collided with the car next to you. Blind spot warning alerts you to the presence of a vehicle to your sides or rear so you know if you're about to make an unsafe lane change. Replace fear and uncertainty with confidence and safety with blind spot warning.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Voice activated integrated navigation system - A to B made easy! Whether it's an errand or a road trip, the voice activated integrated navigation system will guide you to your destination. No more bulky, impossible-to-fold maps, and no more stopping to ask for directions. Just tell it where you want to go, and the voice activated integrated navigation system shows you the right way.

Now available at Hudson Ford, this 2023 Nissan Rouge SV AWD is a versatile and feature-packed compact SUV that's perfect for daily driving, family adventures, and all-weather confidence. Finished in striking Scarlet Ember Tint coat with a Charcoal interior, this Rouge comes equipped with a 1.5L VC-Turbo 3-cylinder engine paired to a smooth CVT automatic transmission and All-Wheel Drive for assured handling on rain-soaked roads and snowy streets alike. With an estimated 28 MPG city/35 MPG highway, it delivers both efficiency and spirited performance.

Inside, the Rouge SV blends comfort with modern technology to elevate every drive. Key features include Android Auto and Apple CarPlay for seamless smartphone integration, adaptive cruise control, heated seats and heated steering wheel, power liftgate, remote start, blind spot monitoring, rear cross-traffic alert, and parking sensors to help make every trip easier and safer. Its spacious. well-appointed cabin provides plenty of room for passengers and cargo -- ideal for road trips or weekend errands.

As a Ford Blue Certified vehicle, this Rouge has passed a detailed 139-point inspection and includes benefits such as a Comprehensive Limited Warranty, roadside assistance, transferrable warranty, money-back guarantee, and 11,000 Ford Pass rewards points to use toward your first maintenance visit --- giving you added peace of mind with your purchase. Ford Blue Certified vehicles are thoroughly inspected, backed by warranty coverage, and offer confidence-boosting protection for buyers seeking quality pre-owned vehicles.

  • 8-Way Power Driver Seat Adjuster
  • Power Driver Lumbar Control Seat Adjuster
  • Remote Start
  • Heated Driver and Front Passenger Seats
  • 120-Volt Power Outlet
  • Hands Free Power Programmable Liftgate
  • Brushed Aluminum Roof Rails
Preferred Equipment Group 3SA
    Safety and Security
    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring

Tuned for the trail, our electrified Accident Free 2023 Jeep Wrangler 4xe Sahara 4X4 looks terrific in Hydro Blue Pearl! Motivated by a TurboCharged 2.0 Liter 4 Cylinder and 2 Electric Motors providing a combined 375hp to an 8 Speed Automatic transmission. The incredibly capable Four Wheel Drive SUV just about does it all with Dana axles, an EV range of nearly 22 miles, and a gas-hybrid mode that sees nearly 20mpg combined. Iconic Jeep styling gives our Wrangler 4xe a bold presence backed by exclusive Sahara graphics, LED lighting, fog lamps, blue tow hooks, 20-inch alloy wheels, full-body fender flares, side steps, rugged skid plates, and a removable top and doors.

Our Sahara cabin encourages inspiring adventures with comfortable McKinley cloth seats, a premium wrapped steering wheel, automatic climate control, cruise control, and keyless access/ignition. First-class technologies include a Uconnect infotainment system with a 7-inch driver display, a 7-inch touchscreen, voice command, Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, Bluetooth, Off-Road Info Pages, and an Alpine sound system.

Jeep's dedication to safer driving shines through with a rearview camera, ABS, stability/traction control, hill-start assist, tire-pressure monitoring, advanced airbags, trailer sway damping, and more. Our Wrangler 4xe Sahara is the plug-in hybrid that's pure Jeep! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Park Chrysler Jeep Used Test Drive Towards Ownership!

description: Check out this 2023 Nissan Rogue SV AWD now available at Walser Nissan Burnsville, located on the south side of Minneapolis and St. Paul and just over an hour north of both Rochester and Mankato, with easy access for drivers coming from Eagan and Apple Valley who want a confident all-wheel-drive crossover without giving up efficiency. With an original MSRP of $33,290, this Rogue adds thoughtful extras like Splash Guards, a Chrome Rear Bumper Protector, and a $435 package that includes Floor Mats, a 1-piece Cargo Area Protector, a Seatback Protector, and a First Aid Kit, which is the sort of everyday usability gear you only miss when it's not there. Under the hood you'll find a 1.5L turbocharged engine paired with an Xtronic CVT and Intelligent All-Wheel Drive with a Drive Mode Dial and terrain modes, and the window sticker rates it at 31 MPG combined and up to 35 MPG on the highway, so commuting or weekend trips around Lakeville or Bloomington stay relatively light on fuel stops. Standard safety tech includes Automatic Emergency Braking with Pedestrian Detection, Rear Automatic Braking, Blind Spot Warning with Blind Spot Intervention, Rear Cross Traffic Alert, Lane Departure Warning with Intelligent Lane Intervention, High Beam Assist, Intelligent Forward Collision Warning, and a RearView Monitor, all supported by LED headlights, LED daytime running lights, LED tail lamps, and dual power heated outside mirrors. Inside, Dual-zone Automatic Temperature Control, a Remote Engine Start System with Intelligent Climate Control, and NissanConnect with Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, SiriusXM, an 8-inch color display, and a Wi-Fi hotspot help keep everyone comfortable and connected. CARFAX designates this as a CARFAX 1-Owner vehicle, and recent maintenance includes an oil and filter change at the Walser Recon Center along with previous oil and filter changes and tire rotations documented at Walser Nissan Burnsville and Valvoline in Eagan, so it's been kept on a steady service rhythm. If you're shopping for a well-equipped Rogue SV AWD with strong safety tech, modern connectivity, and practical add-ons baked in, this one is ready for a closer look---contact us today to schedule your test drive!At Walser, you'll get an exceptional car-buying experience. Our *streamlined process* means you'll work with one dedicated customer specialist to help you find the perfect vehicle. Upfront Pricing on every vehicle ensures you'll *get a great deal without any surprises or gimmicks*. Buy with confidence because you're backed by our *Worry-Free Return & Exchange Policy*.The benefits don't stop there. description:
This 2023 Chevrolet Trailblazer Activ available at Ryan Chevrolet in Buffalo, MN is a smart choice for drivers seeking modern capability, advanced safety technology, and impressive efficiency in a compact SUV. Designed with an adventurous edge, the Trailblazer Activ pairs a bold exterior with a refined and comfortable interior, making it equally suited for daily commuting around Wright County or weekend getaways across Minnesota. Its efficient all-wheel-drive system delivers confident traction in changing road conditions while still achieving excellent fuel economy of over 30 miles per gallon on the highway.
Under the hood, the Trailblazer Activ is engineered for responsive performance and smooth driving dynamics, complemented by a well-tuned suspension and confident handling. Inside, the cabin is thoughtfully designed with quality materials and intuitive technology. An 8-inch touchscreen infotainment system anchors the dashboard and is paired with a premium Bose sound system, providing clear audio whether you are streaming music or navigating local roads. Wireless device charging keeps your cabin clutter-free, while synthetic leather upholstery, a power driver’s seat, heated front seats, and automatic climate control add comfort in every season. Additional conveniences such as a hands-free power liftgate, panoramic sunroof, rear window defroster, 120-volt power outlet, and deep tinted glass further enhance everyday usability.
Safety and driver assistance are key strengths of this Trailblazer Activ. Advanced features include adaptive cruise control, automatic emergency braking, forward collision alert, pedestrian braking, lane keep assist with lane departure warning, lane change alert, automatic high beam headlamps, fog lamps, and a rear vision camera. These systems work together to help provide added confidence and peace of mind on every drive. Keyless entry with push-button start ensures easy access and modern convenience.
This vehicle has a clean vehicle history, is a one-previous-owner trade-in, and has been carefully maintained. Our reconditioning process includes a comprehensive multi-point vehicle inspection with an oil change and a complete interior and exterior detail, ensuring this Trailblazer meets the high standards customers expect from Ryan Chevrolet in Buffalo, MN. A free CARFAX Vehicle History Report is available on our website for added transparency.
Finished with distinctive 17-inch high-gloss black machined aluminum wheels, this 2023 Chevrolet Trailblazer Activ delivers a compelling combination of style, technology, safety, and efficiency. Contact us for availability and a test drive today.
Buy with confidence at Ryan Auto Mall. With over 22,500 reviews, 9 GM Mark of Excellence awards, and 65 MN DealerRater Dealer of the Year honors, our reputation is proven. This pre-owned vehicle includes warranty coverage for added peace of mind. Pricing excludes tax, title, license, and a $350 doc fee. Every vehicle is pre-fitted with PULSE, our rear-end collision deterrent system, available for just $399. Visit us at 911 E Hwy 55 in Buffalo or call 612-326-6209 to schedule your test drive and experience the Ryan difference.

description: Our 2023 Toyota RAV4 LE is a smart, capable SUV with just 39,667 miles and the versatility today's drivers want. This vehicle comes with a SMARTCare Maintenance Plan that includes 2 years/25,000 miles of oil changes, tire rotations, and roadside assistance, and it also has four new tires installed with an approximate value of $825, so it's ready for the road right away. Toyota Gold Certified status adds even more confidence with outstanding long-term coverage.Equipped with all-wheel drive and a brake-actuated limited slip differential, this RAV4 delivers confident traction in a variety of road and weather conditions. LED headlights with automatic high beams, privacy glass, and a rear spoiler give it a clean, modern look. Inside, the cabin is comfortable and practical with supportive cloth seating, a versatile rear seat with pass-through capability, and plenty of cargo flexibility for daily errands or weekend trips.Technology features include Bluetooth connectivity, HD and satellite radio, smart device integration, a WiFi hotspot, and a backup camera. Toyota Safety Sense adds peace of mind with adaptive cruise control, lane departure warning with lane keeping assist, front collision mitigation, and stability control. Reliable, efficient, and well equipped, this RAV4 LE is an excellent choice for commuting, family use, or adventure on the go.

Experience the Pinnacle of Utility and Style with the 2023 Kia Sportage X-Line Premium Package

This stunning 2023 Kia Sportage X-Line Premium Package is a true standout in the crowded SUV market. With its sleek exterior design, advanced technology, and impressive performance capabilities, this vehicle is the perfect blend of form and function.

• ALL WHEEL DRIVE
• TOUCH SCREEN MAP NAVIGATION
• POWER PANORAMIC MOONROOF/SUNROOF
• ANDROID AUTO & APPLE CARPLAY
• USB/AUX PORTS
• HEATED SEATS
• DUAL ZONE AUTO CLIMATE CONTROL
• BLIND SPOT DETECTION
• AIR CONDITIONING
• ALLOY WHEELS
• AUTO HIGHBEAM ASSIST
• AUTOMATIC TRANSMISSION
• BACK UP CAMERA
• CARFAX CERTIFIED GUARANTEE!
• COMES WITH A 100,000 MILE FACTORY WARRANTY
• CRUISE CONTROL
• FORWARD COLLISION AVOIDANCE
• HANDS FREE BLUETOOTH
• KEYLESS ENTRY
• KIA CERTIFIED
• LANE DEPARTURE WARNING SYSTEM
• LANE KEEP ASSIST SYSTEM
• LEATHER
• LOCAL TRADE IN - NEVER A RENTAL!
• ONE OWNER
• POWER DRIVERS SEAT
• POWER LIFTGATE
• POWER WINDOWS, LOCKS AND OUTSIDE MIRRORS
• PUSH BUTTON START - SMART KEY
• REAR CROSS TRAFFIC ALERT
• REMOTE START

The X-Line Premium Package takes the Sportage to new heights, adding premium features like a panoramic sunroof, LED interior lighting, and a smart power liftgate. With its striking Glacial White Pearl exterior, this Sportage is sure to turn heads wherever you go.

Under the hood, you'll find a potent I4 engine mated to an 8-speed automatic transmission and Kia's advanced All-Wheel Drive system. This powertrain delivers an impressive balance of power and efficiency, with EPA-estimated fuel economy ratings of 23 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway.

Inside, the Sportage's cabin is both spacious and luxurious, with premium leatherette seating, a heated steering wheel, and a host of advanced tech features. The standard 12.3-inch touchscreen display provides easy access to navigation, smartphone integration, and a premium audio system.

As a Kia Certified Pre-Owned vehicle, this Sportage has undergone a rigorous 165-point inspection and comes with a comprehensive warranty package. You can drive with confidence, knowing that this SUV has been meticulously maintained and is backed by Kia's commitment to quality.

With transparent pricing, top-rated Google reviews, and the longest-tenured staff in the Twin Cities, you can trust Lupient to make your car buying experience simple, reliable, and worry-free.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2023 Nissan Rogue SL, a versatile and technologically advanced SUV that elevates your driving experience. This stunning vehicle, finished in a sleek White exterior, combines style, performance, and cutting-edge features to meet the demands of the modern driver.

Indulge in the comfort and convenience of the Rogue SL, which boasts an impressive array of premium amenities:

• Heated Leather Seats
• All Wheel Drive
• Tri-Zone HVAC
• ProPILOT Assist with Navi-link
• Bose Premium Audio System
• Radio: AM/FM NissanConnect with Navigation
• Front, Side & Rear Sonar
• Motion Activated Power Liftgate
• Rear Door Sunshades
• Traffic Sign Recognition

Powered by a 1.5L I3 Turbocharged DOHC 12V engine, the Rogue SL delivers a thrilling 201 horsepower, seamlessly transferred to the road through an advanced CVT with Xtronic and AWD system. With an EPA-estimated 28 city/34 highway MPG, this SUV strikes the perfect balance between performance and efficiency.

Step inside the Rogue SL and experience the epitome of modern luxury. The spacious, leather-appointed interior offers ample room for passengers and cargo, while the Tri-Zone HVAC system ensures everyone travels in comfort. The Bose Premium Audio System, with its 10 speakers, including a dual driver subwoofer, delivers a concert-hall-like listening experience.

The Rogue SL's advanced technology features further enhance your driving experience. The NissanConnect system, with a 9-inch color display and multi-touch control, provides seamless integration of your smartphone via Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. The ProPILOT Assist with Navi-link system helps you navigate with confidence, while the Front, Side & Rear Sonar sensors ensure you maneuver with ease.

Safety is paramount in the Rogue SL, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. From the Rear Door Sunshades to the Motion Activated Power Liftgate, every detail has been meticulously designed to provide you and your loved ones with the utmost protection and convenience.

description:
Discover the Allure of the 2023 Nissan Murano SV - Elevating Your Driving Experience

Introducing the 2023 Nissan Murano SV, a captivating crossover that blends style, performance, and cutting-edge technology to elevate your driving experience. With its sophisticated design, advanced features, and exceptional capabilities, this Murano is poised to exceed your expectations and become the perfect companion for your journey.

Indulge in the luxurious amenities that set this Murano apart:

• Heated Leather Seats
• Remote Start
• Bluetooth
• All Wheel Drive
• Blind Spot Warning
• Black Splash Guards
• Heated Door Mirrors
• Midnight Edition Badge
• Illuminated Kickplates
• 20" Gloss Black Aluminum Alloy Wheels

The Murano SV Midnight Edition Package further enhances the vehicle's bold appearance, adding a sophisticated black treatment to the front grille, lower fascia, roof rails, and more, creating a striking contrast that is sure to turn heads.

Beneath the sleek exterior, the Murano's 3.5L V6 DOHC 24V engine, paired with a CVT with Xtronic and All-Wheel Drive, delivers a thrilling and responsive driving experience. With an EPA-estimated 20 city/28 highway MPG, this Murano strikes the perfect balance between power and efficiency, ensuring you can conquer the road with confidence.

Comfort and convenience are paramount in the 2023 Murano SV. The spacious interior features heated leather-appointed seats, a power driver's seat, and dual-zone automatic climate control, creating a sanctuary of relaxation. The NissanConnect system seamlessly integrates your smartphone with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, keeping you connected and entertained on every journey.

Safety is also a top priority, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assist technologies, including Blind Spot Warning, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and Automatic Emergency Braking. These cutting-edge features work tirelessly to help protect you and your passengers, giving you the peace of mind you deserve.

Experience the exceptional craftsmanship, advanced technology, and refined capabilities of the 2023 Nissan Murano SV. This captivating crossover is poised to elevate your driving experience and exceed your every expectation. Visit our showroom today to take this remarkable vehicle for a test drive and discover the difference it can make in your life.

description:
Experience the exceptional 2023 Nissan Rogue SV, a versatile and well-equipped SUV that seamlessly blends style, performance, and advanced technology. With its sleek exterior, spacious interior, and impressive array of features, this Rogue is poised to elevate your driving experience.

Standout features of this Rogue SV include:

• Collision Warning System
• Adaptive Cruise Control
• Blind-Spot Monitors
• Lane Keeping Assist
• Apple CarPlay
• Android Auto
• 4x4/4 Wheel Drive/AWD

In addition, this Rogue comes equipped with a range of premium accessories, such as the Floor Mats with 1-Piece Cargo Area Protector, Black Splash Guards, and the Chrome Rear Bumper Protector, adding both style and functionality.

Powered by a 1.5L I3 Turbocharged DOHC 12V engine, the 2023 Nissan Rogue SV delivers an impressive balance of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 28 city and 35 highway MPG. The Xtronic CVT with Xtronic all-wheel drive system ensures a smooth and confident ride, regardless of the terrain.

Step inside the Rogue SV and experience the exceptional attention to detail. The cabin is thoughtfully designed, with premium cloth seating, a spacious and versatile layout, and a host of advanced technology features, including the NissanConnect infotainment system with seamless smartphone integration.

Safety is a top priority in the Rogue SV, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Automatic Emergency Braking, Rear Parking Sensors, and a Rearview Camera, helping to keep you and your loved ones secure on the road.

Whether you're navigating the daily commute or embarking on weekend adventures, the 2023 Nissan Rogue SV is the perfect companion. With its exceptional blend of style, performance, and technology, this SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience. Visit our showroom today to schedule a test drive and experience the Rogue SV for yourself.

description: Experience the perfect blend of style, performance, and advanced technology with the 2023 Nissan Rogue SV Intelligent AWD. Dressed in a sleek Super Black exterior, this compact SUV commands attention on every road. The refined charcoal interior provides a spacious and comfortable cabin, designed for both driver and passengers alike. Powered by a cutting-edge VC-Turbo 1.5L I-3 gasoline direct injection engine, the Rogue delivers an impressive 201 horsepower, ensuring a dynamic driving experience without compromising fuel efficiency. Equipped with Intelligent All-Wheel Drive, the Rogue ensures optimal traction and stability in various driving conditions, allowing you to drive with confidence. Whether you're commuting to work or embarking on a weekend adventure, the 2023 Nissan Rogue SV is the sophisticated and versatile choice for today's driver. Elevate your journeys with a vehicle that seamlessly merges innovation, performance, and comfort. Discover your next adventure in the 2023 Nissan Rogue SV Intelligent AWD.

This Certified 2023 Honda HR-V Sport, has a Platinum White Pearl exterior and an Black interior color. 39,467 miles. Stock Number 55145A. You can connect with us by calling 956-217-0127. No Accidents! One Owner! Important Package and Feature Information Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

Every mile feels controlled, engaging, and unmistakably Audi.Inside, the Premium Plus cabin surrounds you with modern luxury and thoughtful design. Hands-Free Power Liftgate Package ($595 value)

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Wireless Apple CarPlay/Wireless Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

description:
Parents researching safe, practical family vehicles will find the 2023 Chevrolet Equinox Premier excels at child seat compatibility and overall utility. The rear bench supports up to three car seats thanks to wide spacing and easy-to-access LATCH anchors, while the rear doors open wide for hassle-free loading. Its compact exterior hides a roomy cabin, making it ideal for everyday errands and weekend adventures with kids.

This SUV is tailored for families with young children requiring multiple car seats, as well as those with teens and frequent passengers. Its flexible seating accommodates growing families, and features like heated rear seats and rear USB charging ports ensure comfort and convenience during carpools or road trips. The Equinox also appeals to busy families juggling sports practice and grocery runs, with its power liftgate and versatile cargo space.

With a smooth 1.5L turbo engine and 6-speed automatic transmission, the Equinox delivers gentle acceleration—perfect for not disturbing sleeping little ones—yet provides enough passing power for confident highway merging when the whole family is aboard. Its 26/31 city/highway MPG rating helps stretch the budget for vacations, and the four-wheel independent suspension keeps the ride composed, even on bumpy suburban roads.

Peace of mind is paramount, and this vehicle delivers with a full suite of family-focused safety features. Dual-stage LATCH anchors in the rear outboard seats make installing up to two car seats easy, while a third can be safely installed with the seatbelt in the center. Comprehensive airbag coverage includes front, side, and overhead zones. The Equinox earns top NHTSA and IIHS crash test ratings, and it includes Teen Driver mode for monitoring new drivers. Rear Seat Reminder helps prevent accidental child or item leave-behind, and OnStar emergency communications are always available. Air quality is enhanced through an advanced cabin filtration system, further protecting what matters most.

The Confidence & Convenience II and Infotainment II Packages equip this SUV with features families will use daily. HD Surround Vision and Automatic Front & Rear Parking Assist simplify tight parking situations, while Adaptive Cruise Control makes long journeys less stressful. Perforated leather-appointed seats, heated front and rear outboard seats, ventilated front seats, wireless Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, and a premium 6-speaker audio system turn every ride into a comfortable experience. The power sunroof, memory seat, and hands-free liftgate add luxury and practicality.

Compared to rivals like the Honda CR-V and Toyota RAV4, the Equinox Premier stands out with three easy-access LATCH positions, heated rear seats, and superior in-cabin technology. While some competitors offer more cargo space, they often lack the Equinox’s rear seat reminder and Teen Driver system, making this SUV a safer, more family-friendly choice for peace of mind every day.

Three car seats fit securely in the back thanks to wide spacing and dual LATCH anchors, with a third in the center using the seatbelt. The Equinox is designed for family safety, offering extensive airbag coverage, advanced driver aids, and a highly-rated crash safety record. Rear Seat Reminder is included, helping ensure that nothing precious is left behind. Teen Driver mode lets parents monitor driving habits, supporting safe learning for new drivers.

For families prioritizing safety and convenience, Bayway Chevrolet offers the 2023 Equinox Premier at 5719 Broadway St, Pearland, TX, 77581. Call 281-719-9821 for more details or to schedule a test drive, and discover the peace of mind that comes from protecting what matters most in a truly family-focused SUV.

Powered by a robust 1.3L Ecotec Turbo engine and equipped with a smooth-shifting CVT transmission, the TrailBlazer RS delivers an exhilarating yet efficient ride, with an impressive 29 MPG in the city and 33 MPG on the highway. Its striking Mosaic Black Metallic Two-Tone Roof and 18" High Gloss Black Machined Aluminum wheels create a bold, head-turning presence on the road.

Step inside the cabin and discover a wealth of premium features designed to enhance your comfort and convenience. The Confidence II Package includes Rear Park Assist, providing added peace of mind when maneuvering in tight spaces. The Convenience Package elevates your driving experience with automatic climate control, an 8" touchscreen display, and a 120-volt power outlet.

Connectivity is key in today's world, and the TrailBlazer RS delivers with its Chevrolet Infotainment 3 System, complete with wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. Stay seamlessly connected to your digital life, whether streaming music, accessing navigation, or taking hands-free calls.

Safety is paramount, and the TrailBlazer RS is equipped with a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. From the Rear Park Assist to the Auto High-Beam Headlights, you can navigate the roads with confidence, knowing that your vehicle is looking out for you.

Experience the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology with the 2023 Chevrolet TrailBlazer RS. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional crossover can elevate your driving experience.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with the remarkable 2023 Nissan Ariya EVOLVE+ e-4ORCE. This exceptional electric crossover SUV is the perfect blend of style, performance, and cutting-edge technology, tailored to meet the needs of the modern driver.

Boasting a stunning Green exterior, the Ariya EVOLVE+ e-4ORCE is equipped with an impressive array of features that will elevate your daily commute and weekend adventures. Key highlights include:

• PUSH BUTTON GO
• BACK UP CAMERA
• APPLE CARPLAY/ANDROID AUTO
• ADAPTIVE CRUISE CONTROL
• BLIND SPOT WARNING SYSTEM
• ILLUMINATED KICK PLATES
• CARPETED FLOOR MATS & FIRST AID KIT

With an impressive EPA-estimated 97 MPGe in the city and 86 MPGe on the highway, the Ariya EVOLVE+ e-4ORCE delivers exceptional efficiency and a thrilling all-electric driving experience. The advanced AWD system provides confident handling and control, ensuring a smooth and responsive ride in any condition.

This Nissan Certified pre-owned vehicle has undergone a meticulous 167-point inspection and comes with a comprehensive warranty package, providing you with the peace of mind you deserve. Enjoy the benefits of Roadside Assistance, a Transferable Warranty, and a Carfax Vehicle History Report, along with a 7-year/100,000-mile limited warranty and 1 year of pre-paid maintenance.

Step into the future of automotive technology with the 2023 Nissan Ariya EVOLVE+ e-4ORCE. This exceptional electric crossover offers a driving experience that will exceed your expectations, with a perfect blend of style, efficiency, and advanced features. Visit our showroom today and discover the true potential of this remarkable vehicle.

At our dealership, we are committed to providing our customers with the highest level of service and a seamless purchasing experience. Our knowledgeable sales team is eager to answer any questions you may have and help you find the perfect vehicle to meet your needs. We look forward to the opportunity to earn your business and help you drive away in the 2023 Nissan Ariya EVOLVE+ e-4ORCE of your dreams.

description: Introducing the 2023 Volkswagen Tiguan SE R-Line Black, a perfect blend of sophistication and performance. This stunning SUV features a sleek black exterior complemented by R-Line styling accents, providing a bold and sporty presence on the road. Under the hood, the Tiguan SE is powered by a robust engine designed for an exhilarating driving experience while maintaining exceptional fuel efficiency. The spacious interior comfortably seats up to five passengers, featuring premium materials and advanced technology for a modern driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of a touchscreen infotainment system, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto, ensuring seamless connectivity on all your journeys. Safety is a top priority in the 2023 Tiguan, equipped with advanced driver-assistance features such as adaptive cruise control, blind-spot monitoring, and autonomous emergency braking, giving you peace of mind wherever you go. With its agile handling, ample cargo space, and comprehensive warranty, the Tiguan SE R-Line Black is an ideal choice for families and adventure seekers alike. Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional vehicle-where style meets functionality. Don't miss your chance to own a true masterpiece!

Boasting an impressive array of features, this RAV4 Hybrid Woodland Edition is equipped with:
• AWD/4WD

• Bluetooth

• Rear Backup Camera
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Sport Edition

Elevating your driving experience even further, this Woodland Edition also includes:
• Black Chrome Exhaust Tip

• 100W/120V USB Charger

The Woodland Edition's rugged good looks are complemented by a host of advanced safety features, including Adaptive Cruise Control, Lane Keep Assist, and Tire Pressure Monitoring, providing you with the confidence and peace of mind to tackle any road or trail.

Not only is this RAV4 Hybrid Woodland Edition a true adventurer's dream, but it's also in exceptional condition, having just received new tires and brakes, ensuring a smooth and reliable driving experience.

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

If our vehicle does not pass our inspection, it must be brought up to our retail standards or be disposed to an auto auction. We know that both our competitively priced and highly reconditioned retail vehicle do not get sold, if we do not tailor the sales experience to your needs. We are dedicated to making your buying experience excellent from the time you find our vehicle on line to the time you are taking delivery of your new car.

Our team at Russell & Smith takes pride in providing you with exceptional service and an unmatched experience. Being a family owned and operated business, you can trust you will be treated as one of our own. We have been committed to this promise since 1917. How we can Help Online: Our web experience takes the hassle out of finding the perfect vehicle that is within your budget. Elevate your daily drive with this 2023 Chevy Equinox LT in sleek Sterling Gray Metallic. What makes Russell & Smith retail cars better than our competition? That is easy, the high reconditioning standards we have. If our vehicle does not pass our inspection, it must be brought up to our retail standards or be disposed to an auto auction. We know that both our competitively priced and highly reconditioned retail vehicle do not get sold, if we do not tailor the sales experience to your needs. We are dedicated to making your buying experience excellent from the time you find our vehicle on line to the time you are taking delivery of your new car.

As one of the most popular compact SUVs in its class, the RAV4 LE delivers a well-rounded driving experience tailored for Houston-area commuters, families and weekend travelers alike. With its dependable performance, smart design and strong value, the RAV4 continues to be a top choice for drivers who want capability without sacrificing comfort or efficiency.The 2023 RAV4 LE is engineered to offer confident performance in a variety of driving conditions. Its responsive powertrain provides smooth acceleration and impressive fuel efficiency, whether you're navigating city streets, merging onto the freeway or taking a scenic route through Texas backroads. Toyota's refined suspension helps create a stable, comfortable ride, while the elevated seating position enhances visibility and confidence behind the wheel. Built with durability in mind, this SUV stands ready for daily use, long road trips and everything in between.Inside, the RAV4 LE offers a thoughtfully designed cabin centered around convenience and versatility. Supportive seating, intuitive controls and a spacious layout make it easy for both driver and passengers to settle in and enjoy the ride. The modern infotainment system provides seamless connectivity, clear audio, integrated smartphone compatibility and easy access to navigation and entertainment features. With generous cargo capacity and flexible storage configurations, the RAV4 adapts to grocery runs, road trips, sports gear and family adventures with ease.Toyota continues its commitment to safety with a suite of driver-assist features designed to support awareness and confidence on the road. These smart technologies help monitor surroundings, assist with braking and enhance overall control, giving you added reassurance on busy city roads or during long-distance travel.Low Sonic Price!! description: Introducing the 2018 Ford Fusion SE, a sleek and sophisticated sedan that blends style, performance, and dependability into one irresistible package. With only 59,000 miles on the odometer, this Fusion is primed and ready to deliver countless more miles of driving pleasure. It's not just a car, it's a statement of modern elegance and efficiency. Under the hood, you'll find the heart of this beauty—the EcoBoost 1.5L Turbo I4 engine. With a robust 181 horsepower and 185 lb-ft of torque, this powertrain offers the perfect balance of performance and fuel efficiency. Whether you're cruising down the highway or navigating city streets, the Fusion's engine ensures a smooth, responsive ride every time. Coupled with a 6-Speed Shiftable Automatic transmission, you'll experience seamless gear transitions and the flexibility to adapt to any driving condition with ease. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by an interior that exudes comfort and sophistication. The "other cloth" seating provides a plush, inviting atmosphere for both driver and passengers. Every detail inside the Fusion SE is designed to enhance your driving experience, from the intuitive dashboard layout to the ample legroom and headspace that ensures every journey is as comfortable as it is enjoyable. One of the standout features of this 2018 Ford Fusion SE is its recognition in the J.D. Power and Associates's Vehicle Dependability Study (VDS) as a Top Model. This accolade is a testament to the Fusion's exceptional reliability and long-term quality, giving you peace of mind that you're investing in a vehicle that's built to last. Dependability is key when choosing a car, and the Fusion SE has proven itself time and again. Beyond its impressive performance and reliability, the Fusion SE is also equipped with a host of manufacturer options and packages that elevate your driving experience. While specific options aren't listed, the Fusion SE typically includes features like advanced safety systems, state-of-the-art infotainment, and convenient driver-assist technologies that make every drive safer and more enjoyable. The exterior of the 2018 Ford Fusion SE is a masterpiece of modern design. Its sleek lines and aerodynamic profile not only catch the eye but also contribute to its outstanding fuel efficiency. The Fusion's bold grille and signature lighting elements make a striking impression, ensuring you turn heads wherever you go. In summary, the 2018 Ford Fusion SE is more than just a car—it's your ticket to a world of driving excellence. With its low mileage, award-winning dependability, and a perfect blend of performance and comfort, this Fusion is ready to meet all your driving needs. Whether you're commuting to work, embarking on a weekend getaway, or simply running errands around town, the Fusion SE promises to deliver an exceptional driving experience every time you get behind the wheel. Don't miss your chance to own this outstanding vehicle. The 2018 Ford Fusion SE is waiting for you, ready to redefine your expectations of what a sedan can be. Schedule a test drive today and experience the perfect fusion of style, performance, and reliability for yourself. Your dream car is just one drive away!

Stock: H01955 2011 Audi S4 Premium Plus- Now Available at Hickory Used Car Superstore! If you're looking for a vehicle that delivers on performance, utility, comfort, or value, this 2011 Audi S4 Premium Plus may be just the ticket! Vehicle Highlights: Navigation Package with Camera ($2,550 value)
  • HD Radio
  • Color Driver Information System
  • Navigation Plus System with 3G MMI
  • Rear Back Up Camera
Comfort
  • Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions - That's hot. Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions provide more targeted warmth so you can get comfortable quicker in cold weather. If you have lower body pain, you might also be soothed by the heat while you drive. No matter the weather, find comfort in heated driver and front passenger seat cushions.
Convenience
  • Cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Meet your ultimate co-pilot, cruise control.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Voice activated integrated navigation system - A to B made easy! Whether it's an errand or a road trip, the voice activated integrated navigation system will guide you to your destination. No more bulky, impossible-to-fold maps, and no more stopping to ask for directions. Just tell it where you want to go, and the voice activated integrated navigation system shows you the right way.

description:
Experience the exceptional 2022 Hyundai Palisade SEL, a remarkable SUV that combines style, comfort, and advanced technology to elevate your driving experience. With its sleek exterior, spacious interior, and impressive performance, this Palisade is the perfect companion for your adventures.

Highlighted features of this Palisade SEL include:
• Premium Package
• Premium Package P3
• Hands-Free Smart Liftgate
• Power 3rd Row Seating
• Heated Steering Wheel
• Driver's Seat Integrated Memory System
• Radio: AM/FM/MP3 Premium Audio System
• 10.25" Display Screen
• Apple CarPlay and Android Auto
• Wireless Phone Charger
• Acoustic Front Side Glass
• Highway Drive Assist I

The Palisade's luxurious interior offers an unparalleled level of comfort and convenience. Slide into the premium leather-wrapped seats and let the driver's seat memory system position the seat and mirrors to your preferred settings. The heated steering wheel and second-row seats provide warmth on chilly days, while the power-folding and reclining third-row seats offer versatility to accommodate your passengers and cargo.

Beneath the sleek exterior, the Palisade's 3.8-liter V6 engine and all-wheel-drive system deliver a smooth and confident ride, whether you're navigating city streets or exploring the open road. With an EPA-estimated 24 mpg on the highway, this SUV offers impressive fuel efficiency to complement its powerful performance.

The Palisade's advanced technology features further enhance your driving experience. The 10.25-inch touchscreen display seamlessly integrates with your smartphone through Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, allowing you to access your favorite apps, music, and navigation with ease. The Hyundai Blue Link connected car system provides additional convenience and peace of mind, with features like remote start, vehicle diagnostics, and emergency assistance.

Safety is also a top priority in the Palisade, with a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Highway Drive Assist I, Front Parking Sensors, and Ultrasonic Rear Occupant Alert, to help keep you and your loved ones protected on the road.

Experience the unparalleled combination of style, comfort, and technology in the 2022 Hyundai Palisade SEL. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional SUV can elevate your driving experience.

FREE LIFETIME WARRANTY

This 2022 Nissan Rogue Sport SL is a standout in the compact SUV segment, offering a winning combination of style, capability, and advanced features. With its sleek red exterior and well-appointed interior, this Rogue Sport is sure to turn heads wherever you go.

Key features include:
• Navigation system: NissanConnect Navigation
• 6 Speakers
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• Air Conditioning
• Power driver seat
• Blind Spot Warning
• Rear Parking Sensors

The Rogue Sport's 2.0L DOHC engine, paired with a smooth-shifting CVT and available Intelligent All-Wheel Drive, delivers a responsive and efficient driving experience. With an EPA-estimated 24 city/30 highway MPG, this SUV will help you go further on every tank.

This Nissan Certified Pre-Owned vehicle has undergone a rigorous 167-point inspection and comes with a comprehensive warranty, roadside assistance, and a CARFAX Vehicle History Report. You can trust that this Rogue Sport is ready to provide years of reliable and enjoyable ownership.

The spacious interior offers comfortable seating for five, along with ample cargo space to accommodate your active lifestyle. The impressive list of standard and available features, including the NissanConnect infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, ensures you'll enjoy every drive.

Safety is also a top priority, with advanced driver-assistance technologies like Blind Spot Warning, Rear Parking Sensors, and Automatic Emergency Braking to help keep you and your passengers secure.

With its compelling blend of style, capability, and technology, this 2022 Nissan Rogue Sport SL is an exceptional value in the pre-owned market. Visit our showroom today to experience it for yourself and discover why it could be the perfect fit for your next adventure.

2022 GMC Terrain AT4
VIN: 3GKALYEV7NL312717

This 2022 GMC Terrain AT4 is a great option for buyers who want a compact SUV with a tougher look and added all wheel drive capability. It blends everyday comfort with a more confident stance and added traction for changing road conditions.

Performance
Powered by a 1.5L turbocharged engine that delivers smooth responsive acceleration. The all wheel drive system provides added confidence in rain gravel and light off road situations while still maintaining a comfortable ride for daily driving.

Exterior
The AT4 trim gives this Terrain a more rugged appearance with bold styling cues and a stance that stands out. It looks right at home in the driveway or heading out of town for the weekend.

Interior
Comfortable well designed cabin with durable materials and supportive seating. The interior layout is practical and easy to live with whether you are commuting or loading up for a trip.

Technology
Well equipped with a touchscreen infotainment system that includes Bluetooth Apple CarPlay and Android Auto capability. Steering wheel mounted controls allow you to manage audio phone and vehicle information with ease. Multiple USB ports keep devices charged for everyone on board.

Safety
Equipped with GMC safety features designed to support confident driving. Features include forward collision alert automatic emergency braking lane keep assist with lane departure warning following distance indicator and a rear vision camera to assist with parking and backing up.

Why Buy?
The Terrain AT4 offers a unique combination of compact SUV size all wheel drive capability and GMC refinement. With low miles for the year and local servicing this is a strong choice for drivers who want versatility without moving into a larger SUV.

description: Make a bold impression on every journey with this striking Platinum Gray Metallic 2022 Volkswagen Tiguan 2.0T SE R-Line Black. This SUV is designed for those who want a sporty, sophisticated look without sacrificing the versatility of a family vehicle. As a CARFAX One-Owner with a Clean CARFAX, it has been meticulously maintained and is ready to deliver the premium German engineering that Volkswagen is known for.The R-Line Black trim sets itself apart with an aggressive, "blacked-out" personality. It features 19-inch black alloy wheels, a signature R-Line front bumper, and black accents on the roof rails and window trim. Under the hood, the 2.0L Turbocharged engine provides a punchy and responsive drive, while the 4MOTION All-Wheel Drive (AWD) system ensures you have the traction and stability to handle Arkansas' changing weather and backroads with total confidence.Inside, the cabin is a masterclass in modern comfort and style. You'll be greeted by Perforated V-Tex Leatherette Seating Surfaces and Heated Front Comfort Seats that are perfect for those crisp mornings. The interior feels open and airy thanks to the Power Moonroof, while the 15-color ambient lighting allows you to set the perfect mood for every drive. High-end touches like the leather-wrapped sport steering wheel and leather shift knob elevate the entire experience.Technology is seamlessly integrated into your daily routine. The Tiguan features the VW Digital Cockpit, a high-resolution digital instrument cluster that puts all your important driving information front and center. Staying connected is easy with the MIB3 Composition Media system, offering Wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto so you can access your favorite apps without reaching for a cord. Plus, the Power Liftgate and rain-sensing wipers add an extra layer of convenience to your busy lifestyle.Safety remains a top priority with VWs advanced driver-assistance features. This Tiguan comes equipped with Adaptive Cruise Control, an Exterior Parking Camera, and a comprehensive airbag system to protect you and your passengers. Whether you're carpooling to practice or heading out for a weekend getaway, this 2022 Tiguan SE R-Line Black offers the perfect blend of safety, style, and sporty performance.Faster. Simpler. More Transparent. Superior Automotive Group has helped thousands of customers find the right car by leveraging one of Arkansas' largest selections of new and pre-owned vehicles at unparalleled prices. Yet, it's our extra-mile customer service and uncommonly candid and respectful staff that have won the trust and loyalty of Arkansas drivers for 30 years. Come visit one of our Superior dealerships today and let us exceed your expectations.
